Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I was left at the altar in front
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.01,0:00:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,of the entire town. My
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.40,0:00:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,fiance vanished. The guests
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.19,0:00:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,laughed
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.66,0:00:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,behind my
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.83,0:00:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,back, and the wedding debt fell
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.71,0:00:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,on me like a sentence.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.61,0:00:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Within days, I lost my job,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.91,0:00:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,my home, and what little dignity
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.16,0:00:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I had left. That
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.29,0:00:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,was when Ludovico Caracelo
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.93,0:00:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,appeared. The most
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.07,0:00:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,feared man in Providence offered
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.93,0:00:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,me away out. He'd pay
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.15,0:00:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,everything. Clear my name, and
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.56,0:00:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,protect me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.45,0:00:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,If I agreed to be his wife on
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.25,0:00:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,paper, I thought I was
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.61,0:00:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,entering a cold contract. But
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.45,0:00:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,soon I
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.83,0:00:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,discovered my fiance hadn't just
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.79,0:00:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,run away, and that
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.89,0:00:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Ludovico knew far more than he
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.87,0:00:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,let on.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.55,0:00:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The bouquet trembled in my hand,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.40,0:00:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,and I couldn't decide
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.61,0:00:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,whether it was the weight of the
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.96,0:00:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,roses,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.77,0:00:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,or the weight of the waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.33,0:00:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Providence church smelled of
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.83,0:00:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,melted wax and old lilies. That
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.33,0:00:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,two
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.57,0:00:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,sweet perfume that clung to the
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.32,0:00:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,throat. The priest had
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.57,0:00:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,already checked the clock three
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.31,0:00:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,times. The first
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.85,0:00:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,he smiled at me the way you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.38,0:01:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,tried to call my child. The
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.91,0:01:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,second. He turned his face to
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.69,0:01:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,avoid my eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.03,0:01:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The third, he didn't even bother
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.92,0:01:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,pretending anymore. All of
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.46,0:01:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Providence was seated behind me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.61,0:01:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I felt the murmur rise up the
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.28,0:01:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,back of my white dress like a
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.94,0:01:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,cold current, a whisper that
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.55,0:01:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,swelled
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.95,0:01:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,with every passing minute. The
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.41,0:01:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,women in the fifth row had
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.67,0:01:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,stopped disguising their
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.84,0:01:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,whispering.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.93,0:01:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,One of them laughed low, held
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.47,0:01:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,back, and I heard it because I
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.06,0:01:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,heard everything in that moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.75,0:01:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The rest of the fans, the
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.26,0:01:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,shuffle of feet, the tick-tock
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.07,0:01:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,of the old clock at the back of
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.95,0:01:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,the
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.13,0:01:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,nave, a delmo had set the time
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.11,0:01:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,for 11 o'clock. It was ten to
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.02,0:01:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,noon. Narina was right behind
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.93,0:01:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,me,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.27,0:01:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,in the first row, squeezing the
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.85,0:01:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,back of my hand as if she could
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.43,0:01:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,hold me in place by the strength
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.07,0:01:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,of
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.17,0:01:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,her fingers. She didn't say
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.86,0:01:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,anything. Narina had a comment
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.74,0:01:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,for everything, a joke even at a
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.75,0:01:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,funeral.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.81,0:01:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And her silence right then was
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.54,0:01:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,the most terrifying thing that
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.26,0:01:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,happened to me that morning. I
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.99,0:01:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,closed my eyes,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.85,0:01:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,took a deep breath, counted to
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.85,0:01:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,ten. I opened my eyes, and the
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.85,0:01:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,church door was still empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.31,0:02:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I, Alanda, Narina murmured close
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.36,0:02:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,to my ear. Sweetheart, don't
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.16,0:02:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,talk. My voice came out steady,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.63,0:02:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,low, but steady. If you talk,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.53,0:02:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll fall apart. She squeezed my
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.62,0:02:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,hand again, and the bell began.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.23,0:02:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,One toll, noon, two tolls. The
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.14,0:02:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,priest came down from the altar
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.12,0:02:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,and walked over to me. Three
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.91,0:02:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,tolls.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.29,0:02:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The women in the fifth row were
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.63,0:02:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,no longer laughing. Four tolls.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.97,0:02:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Five, six, eleven, twelve. The
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.23,0:02:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,bell
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.53,0:02:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,told for the last time, and the
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.26,0:02:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,echo hung in the church's
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.65,0:02:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,vaulted ceiling like something
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.32,0:02:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,dirty,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.21,0:02:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,ugly to look at. No one moved,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.31,0:02:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,no one coughed. All of
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.84,0:02:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Providence held its breath at
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.87,0:02:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.21,0:02:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And I felt in my shoulders the
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.92,0:02:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,exact moment the town
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.11,0:02:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,understood, collectively, that I
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.93,0:02:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,had been abandoned.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.01,0:02:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The priest stopped in front of
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.08,0:02:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,me, hands folded. There was pity
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.28,0:02:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,in his eyes, and pity is the
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.21,0:02:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,one thing a bride doesn't know
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.12,0:02:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,where to put. My child, no. I
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.96,0:02:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,clutched the bouquet to my
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.61,0:02:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,chest.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.43,0:02:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to say anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.08,0:03:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I turned my back on him. Facing
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.74,0:03:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,the altar was easier than facing
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.44,0:03:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Providence,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.55,0:03:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,but the church had only one way
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.38,0:03:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,out, and that way passed by
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.97,0:03:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,every familiar face. Every stare
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.85,0:03:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,from those who had come to see
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.48,0:03:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,exactly what they were now
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.89,0:03:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,seeing. Narina stood up with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.63,0:03:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.79,0:03:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,coming with you. She said, one
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.10,0:03:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,step at a time. I started
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.02,0:03:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,walking, one step, then another.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.48,0:03:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The dress
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.17,0:03:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,dragged behind me. And every
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.72,0:03:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,inch of that fabric weighed like
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.48,0:03:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,a remnant of what I had imagined
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.25,0:03:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,that
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.47,0:03:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,morning would be. I had imagined
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.52,0:03:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,laughter. I had imagined a shy
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.44,0:03:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,kiss at the altar. I had
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.98,0:03:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,imagined
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.49,0:03:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,a delmo squeezing my elbow with
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.85,0:03:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,that nervous way of his
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.60,0:03:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,whispering, I'm here, I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.96,0:03:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,A delmo
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.49,0:03:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,hadn't come. I passed the third
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.56,0:03:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,row. Mrs. Marchetti, my neighbor
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.70,0:03:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,for 10 years, lowered her head.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.17,0:03:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I passed the fifth row, and no
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.85,0:03:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,one was laughing anymore. I
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.36,0:03:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,passed the distant cousin a
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.87,0:03:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,delmo
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.15,0:03:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,had invited at the last minute,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.85,0:03:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,and he avoided my eyes with a
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.43,0:03:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,haste that almost broke me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.23,0:03:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Narina held my arm. Look ahead,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.37,0:04:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,just ahead. We reached the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.58,0:04:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The sunlight outside hit my
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.44,0:04:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,eyes,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.23,0:04:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,and for a moment I saw nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.27,0:04:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,And in that white blaze of
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.97,0:04:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,light, I almost believed I was
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.94,0:04:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,going to
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.47,0:04:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,morning that it had all been a
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.34,0:04:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,bad last minute dream. It
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.89,0:04:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,wasn't. I went down the stone
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.69,0:04:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,staircase slowly,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.33,0:04:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,because going down fast was
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.91,0:04:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,admitting that I wanted to run,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.73,0:04:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,and I had decided without
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.20,0:04:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,deciding
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.67,0:04:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,that Providence would not see me
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.96,0:04:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,run. The stones were worn in the
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.25,0:04:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,middle, the iron railing
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.97,0:04:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,darkened by age. Each step
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.43,0:04:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,caused the same effort as a
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.94,0:04:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,breath. A yellow taxi stopped at
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.73,0:04:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,the bottom,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.35,0:04:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,at the corner of the square. I
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.59,0:04:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,hadn't called it. Narina had. I
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.90,0:04:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,got in. She got in after me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.27,0:04:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Federal Hill, she told the
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.85,0:04:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,driver. End of at wells near
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.56,0:04:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Salvis Bakery. The driver looked
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.50,0:04:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,at me in
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.99,0:04:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,the rear view mirror. Saw the
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.78,0:04:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,white dress. Saw my face and
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.52,0:04:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,didn't ask anything. He started
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.44,0:04:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,the car
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.87,0:04:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,in silence. I rested my forehead
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.95,0:04:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,against the glass. The city
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.70,0:04:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,rushed past outside. The statue
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.72,0:04:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,in the
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.11,0:04:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,square. Old Salvis Bakery. The
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.85,0:05:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,corner where Adelmo had kissed
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.60,0:05:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,me for the first time three
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.17,0:05:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.17,0:05:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,On that corner, he had told me
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.65,0:05:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,he would love me until the day
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.14,0:05:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,the world forgot how to turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.05,0:05:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The world had turned just fine
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.76,0:05:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,that morning. I got home before
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.53,0:05:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I felt my feet. Narina opened
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.19,0:05:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,the door to my apartment. Went
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.93,0:05:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,in first. Started turning on
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.56,0:05:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,lights. I stood in the middle of
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.42,0:05:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,the
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.59,0:05:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,living room, still in the dress,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.40,0:05:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,still holding the bouquet, and
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.09,0:05:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,looked around like someone
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.56,0:05:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,visiting a
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.13,0:05:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,stranger's house. Everything was
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.08,0:05:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,still in place. The cup I had
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.84,0:05:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,washed before leaving. The book
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.73,0:05:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,left
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.97,0:05:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,open on the arm of the sofa. The
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.05,0:05:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,empty vase waiting for the
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.74,0:05:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,wedding flowers. I sat on the
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.62,0:05:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,floor. I just sat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.31,0:05:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The dress billowed around me
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.74,0:05:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,like a cloud, and I didn't cry
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.28,0:05:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,because crying was asking too
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.77,0:05:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,much
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.97,0:05:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,of the body at that hour. I just
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.83,0:05:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,sat there with the bouquet in my
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.68,0:05:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,lap and stared at the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.69,0:05:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Narina sat down next to me on
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.35,0:05:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,the floor. Without taking off
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.00,0:05:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,her shoes, without smoothing her
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.83,0:05:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,dress.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.17,0:05:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,She rested her head on my
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.80,0:05:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,shoulder and stayed. He'll show
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.83,0:05:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,up. I said,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.05,0:06:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,something happened. An accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.42,0:06:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Something. Narina didn't answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.80,0:06:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Narina. No. What do you mean no?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.47,0:06:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not going to show up,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.73,0:06:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Iolanda. She lifted her head and
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.28,0:06:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,looked me in the eye. If it had
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.78,0:06:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,been
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.97,0:06:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,an accident, someone would have
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.62,0:06:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,called. If something had
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.90,0:06:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,happened, his family would be at
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.60,0:06:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,the church.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.71,0:06:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,No one was there. No one. I
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.22,0:06:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,stayed quiet. She was right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.82,0:06:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That morning, none of the
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.15,0:06:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,mothers. Not his brother. No
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.19,0:06:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,one. I had seen it. And I hadn't
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.52,0:06:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,seen it. Sunday passed without
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.70,0:06:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,my
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.85,0:06:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,remembering it. Monday morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.46,0:06:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,the phone rang. The principal of
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.12,0:06:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,the school where I'd been
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.41,0:06:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,teaching
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.83,0:06:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,literature for four years called
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.98,0:06:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,me by my full surname with a
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.86,0:06:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,strange formality. And I already
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.01,0:06:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,knew before she finished the
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.80,0:06:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,sentence. Iolanda, it's not a
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.66,0:06:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,good time to keep a teacher
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.39,0:06:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,involved in
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.09,0:06:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,scandal. Scandal? I leaned
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.11,0:06:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,against the kitchen wall. I was
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.53,0:06:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,jilted Mrs. Peretti. I wasn't
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.78,0:06:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,caught stealing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.79,0:06:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Silence on the other end. Then
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.87,0:07:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,the mothers are talking. You
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.81,0:07:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,understand? A teacher needs an
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.89,0:07:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,intact
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.31,0:07:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,reputation. Reputation. I
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.82,0:07:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,repeated. The reputation of a
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.56,0:07:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,woman who was humiliated in
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.19,0:07:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,public is the
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.97,0:07:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,reputation she lost. Iolanda,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.84,0:07:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,please, please, I said. Yes,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.62,0:07:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,please, my
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.61,0:07:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,hung up. I stood in the kitchen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.33,0:07:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,My hands still on the phone. And
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.78,0:07:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,felt nothing. No anger, no
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.77,0:07:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,shock, no tears, just a very
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.91,0:07:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,polite emptiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.85,0:07:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Like the emptiness of a room
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.19,0:07:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,after the guests have gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.48,0:07:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Tuesday morning, the collectors
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.96,0:07:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,began.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.75,0:07:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The first one showed up at
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.28,0:07:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,eight. In a dress shirt and
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.87,0:07:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,carrying a black briefcase. And
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.70,0:07:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,said my
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.11,0:07:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,name over the inner com with a
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.94,0:07:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,casualness that froze my blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.83,0:07:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,He came up. Sat in my living
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.54,0:07:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,room like
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.09,0:07:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,someone who'd been there before.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.15,0:07:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Open the briefcase and handed me
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.22,0:07:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,a paper. You signed here. His
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.09,0:07:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,finger stopped beneath my
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.69,0:07:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,signature. Next to a delmos.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.47,0:07:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Wedding paid for with borrowed
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.39,0:07:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,money.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.33,0:07:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,$12,000. Do in 30 days. I didn't
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.86,0:07:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,sign any loan. He turned the
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.08,0:08:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,paper toward me. It was my
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.14,0:08:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,handwriting.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.65,0:08:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It was my signature. It was
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.20,0:08:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,right there. Beneath a line of
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.93,0:08:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,text I didn't remember reading.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.71,0:08:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Because now that I looked
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.38,0:08:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,closely, the signature had been
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.44,0:08:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,collected in the pile.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.45,0:08:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Along with the ceremony
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.70,0:08:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,paperwork. The day a delmos
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.16,0:08:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,asked me to sign just some
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.57,0:08:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,boring forms.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.65,0:08:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Love from the venue. I had
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.19,0:08:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,signed without reading. The man
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.03,0:08:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,waited for me to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.29,0:08:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,When I did, he closed the
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.91,0:08:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,briefcase. You have 30 days. If
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.92,0:08:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,you'd rather pay an
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.15,0:08:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,installments,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.07,0:08:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,there's interest. If you'd
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.76,0:08:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,rather negotiate, there are
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.52,0:08:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,partners. Take your pick. He
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.34,0:08:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,stood up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.93,0:08:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,We're watching. He left. I
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.43,0:08:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,didn't move for a stretch of
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.04,0:08:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,time. I can't measure.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.87,0:08:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I went to the window and
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.36,0:08:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,saw his car parked across the
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.85,0:08:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,street. I kept watching. He
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.24,0:08:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,didn't look
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.81,0:08:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,up. He didn't need to. He had
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.69,0:08:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,already looked at me enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.50,0:08:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That afternoon, the second man
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.44,0:08:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,showed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.45,0:08:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Wednesday morning the third.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.91,0:08:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Thursday morning, the eviction
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.47,0:08:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,noticed taped to the apartment
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.03,0:08:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,door.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.69,0:08:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Narina arrived that night with a
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.43,0:09:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,grocery bag. And the serious
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.95,0:09:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,face she almost never wore.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.41,0:09:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,She set the bag on the table,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.21,0:09:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,pulled out a bottle of wine,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.94,0:09:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,pulled out a butter knife. I
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.68,0:09:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,brought
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.11,0:09:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,wine and a butter knife. She
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.11,0:09:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,said, pick first. I laughed
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.03,0:09:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,before I realized I was
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.67,0:09:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,laughing. It was an
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.03,0:09:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,ugly laugh, short, lasting a
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.91,0:09:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,second. But it was a laugh. And
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.98,0:09:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Narina recognized it the way you
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.13,0:09:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,recognize a friend's voice after
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.19,0:09:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,years. Butter knife. I answered.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.25,0:09:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't handle wine tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.05,0:09:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,She set the wine aside. Set
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.05,0:09:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,down. Took off her shoes. Do you
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.43,0:09:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,have anywhere to go? No. Do you
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.73,0:09:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,have
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.03,0:09:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,money? No. Do you have a plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.97,0:09:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Narina. If I had a plan, I
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.65,0:09:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,wouldn't be holding a butter
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.46,0:09:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,knife.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.25,0:09:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,She squeezed my arm. Stayed like
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.28,0:09:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,that for a while. You're staying
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.31,0:09:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,with me. She said,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.71,0:09:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,as long as you need. My couch is
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.73,0:09:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,ugly, but it's mine. I nodded
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.56,0:09:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,slowly. I didn't know if I was
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.45,0:09:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,thanking her or refusing. Both
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.52,0:09:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,things at once, maybe. She
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.32,0:09:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,stayed late.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.61,0:09:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Cooked pasta with whatever was
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.45,0:10:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,in the pantry. Made me eat three
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.42,0:10:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,forkfuls.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.19,0:10:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Took the wedding dress off the
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.57,0:10:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,hanger where it had hung since
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.94,0:10:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Saturday and carried it away
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.23,0:10:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,without
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.55,0:10:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,asking me. Tomorrow I'll burn
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.68,0:10:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,it. She set it the door or
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.59,0:10:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,donated to charity. You decide
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.79,0:10:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,later.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.75,0:10:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I decided later. E. Wednesday
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.61,0:10:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,morning and envelope arrived. It
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.67,0:10:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,was on the floor by the door
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.47,0:10:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,when
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.73,0:10:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,went down to get the newspaper
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.30,0:10:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,out of habit. Not because I
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.71,0:10:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,wanted to read the news,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.39,0:10:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,but because going down the
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.68,0:10:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,stairs was the only gesture of
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.16,0:10:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,the day that still felt like
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.54,0:10:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.23,0:10:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The envelope was of thick paper,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.54,0:10:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,the color of old cream, no
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.42,0:10:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,stamp, no postmark.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.29,0:10:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Just my name written in the
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.99,0:10:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,center. In firm tall
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.25,0:10:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,handwriting, slightly slanted to
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.26,0:10:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,the right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.49,0:10:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Eolanda, Marcecano. No one wrote
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.48,0:10:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,my full name like that. Not even
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.47,0:10:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,my father wrote my full name
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.21,0:10:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,like that. When he was still
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.93,0:10:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,alive, I went up the stairs
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.59,0:10:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,slowly. Satted the kitchen
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.18,0:10:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,table,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.11,0:10:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,opened the envelope carefully as
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.81,0:10:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,if something might escape from
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.41,0:10:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,inside it. There was only a
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.84,0:10:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,card.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.63,0:11:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Cafe Veccia Roma. Tomorrow. 5pm.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.23,0:11:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps I have a solution for
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.59,0:11:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.07,0:11:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,L.C. I stared at the three
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.02,0:11:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,letters. L.C. Two initials an
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.19,0:11:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,period at the end. Like someone
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.51,0:11:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,who
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.73,0:11:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,economizes even with letters.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.32,0:11:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Providence had three ways of
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.85,0:11:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,pronouncing those initials.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.33,0:11:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And all three meant the same
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.11,0:11:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,person. Lutavico Caracolo. The
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.02,0:11:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,man the whole town bowed its
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.80,0:11:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,head to.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.75,0:11:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The man my father had forbidden
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.35,0:11:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,me to look at when I was a
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.69,0:11:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,child. And saw a procession of
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.23,0:11:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,black
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.49,0:11:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,cars passing down at Wells
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.16,0:11:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Avenue. Don't look, Eolanda. He
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.15,0:11:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,had said, that car in the middle
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.20,0:11:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,is the
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.59,0:11:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,car we pretend doesn't exist. I
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.75,0:11:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,was little and I looked anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.90,0:11:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw no one. The glass was too
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.06,0:11:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.85,0:11:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that same man had written my
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.68,0:11:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,name with his own hand. He knew
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.46,0:11:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,my address. He knew of my
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.03,0:11:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,debt. He probably knew more
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.63,0:11:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,things about me than my
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.99,0:11:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,ex-fiance I knew. I set the card
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.88,0:11:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,down on the table.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.47,0:11:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I ran my finger slowly over the
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.77,0:11:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,L. The ink still smelled almost,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.15,0:11:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,almost, or maybe it was my
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.08,0:11:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.71,0:12:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Picturing that fresh ink as a
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.44,0:12:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,way of him being closer. I
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.00,0:12:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,closed my eyes. I thought of the
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.91,0:12:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,eviction noticed tape to the
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.32,0:12:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,door. I thought of the man with
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.87,0:12:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,a black briefcase watching my
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.33,0:12:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,building
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.73,0:12:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,from across the street. I
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.27,0:12:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,thought of Mrs. Pairetti calling
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.25,0:12:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,me miss with disgust. I thought
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.17,0:12:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,of
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.29,0:12:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Nareena on her ugly couch and
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.11,0:12:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,how much she deserved to sleep
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.00,0:12:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,in peace without a ruined friend
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.01,0:12:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,breathing in her living room. I
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.90,0:12:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,opened my eyes. I didn't go to
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.74,0:12:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,the cafe because I wanted to.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.85,0:12:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I went because I had nowhere
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.46,0:12:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,left to run. Cafe Veccia Roma
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.13,0:12:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,sat on a corner of the old
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.62,0:12:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,neighborhood
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.31,0:12:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,where time had decided at some
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.52,0:12:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,point to stop passing. Dark
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.51,0:12:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,wooden doors, smoked glass
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.42,0:12:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,windows,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.01,0:12:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,a discreet bell that rang when I
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.91,0:12:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,pushed the door open, and the
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.64,0:12:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,noise inside dropped.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.53,0:12:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It didn't drop because of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.16,0:12:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,All the stairs at the table
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.67,0:12:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,shifted. In a small,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.80,0:12:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,synchronized
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.47,0:12:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,movement toward the table at the
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.32,0:12:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,back, and the table at the back
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.11,0:12:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,had a man sitting at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.71,0:12:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Ludovico Caracciolo was dressed
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.56,0:12:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,in dark from shoulders to shoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.48,0:13:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,A suit cut with precision.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.71,0:13:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,A white shirt open at the top
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.47,0:13:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,button, no tie. A cup of coffee
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.35,0:13:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,resting in his right hand. His
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.17,0:13:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,wrist
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.47,0:13:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,exposed, an old watch with a
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.38,0:13:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,worn strap. He raised his eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.43,0:13:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,when the bell rang, and saw me
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.48,0:13:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,before
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.89,0:13:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I decided what to do with my
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.69,0:13:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,feet. Dark hair combed back. Two
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.75,0:13:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,days' worth of stubble. His eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.81,0:13:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,were
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.07,0:13:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,the worst. Eyes that already
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.79,0:13:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,knew of me before I arrived. As
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.70,0:13:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,if he had memorized my face
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.36,0:13:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,before
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.73,0:13:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I even reached the door. I
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.34,0:13:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,walked to the table. He didn't
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.19,0:13:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,stand. He didn't pull out the
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.98,0:13:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,chair.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.75,0:13:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,He just watched me come, and the
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.83,0:13:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,whole cafe watched me come with
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.84,0:13:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,him. I sat. Miss Marcie
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.89,0:13:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,His voice was low. Deeper than I
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.05,0:13:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,had expected. Words spaced out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.15,0:13:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Like someone choosing them one
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.17,0:13:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,at
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.31,0:13:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,a time and giving up on the ones
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.40,0:13:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,he didn't need. Mr. Caracciolo,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.42,0:13:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I set my purse on my lap.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.59,0:13:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You know all of Providence is
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.23,0:13:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,looking at this table. All of
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.86,0:13:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Providence looks at any table I
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.61,0:13:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,sit at.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.31,0:13:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,He brought the cup to his lips.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.42,0:13:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Took a small sip. It's not about
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.60,0:14:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,you. What a relief. The corner
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.65,0:14:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,of his mouth twitched slightly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.39,0:14:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't a smile. It was the
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.02,0:14:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,sketch of a thought he decided
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.70,0:14:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,not
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.87,0:14:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,to finish. A waiter appeared
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.53,0:14:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,hand behind his back, bent
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.08,0:14:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,enough to be respectful. What
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.80,0:14:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,will you have
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.57,0:14:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,ma'am? Coffee. Black. No sugar
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.79,0:14:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,today. The waiter nodded and
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.86,0:14:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,disappeared. Lutavico watched me
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.23,0:14:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,or did he say anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.41,0:14:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You called for me. I
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.67,0:14:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,straightened my shoulders. I'm
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.56,0:14:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,here. If you have
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.63,0:14:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,something to say, say it. You
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.31,0:14:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,don't like preamble. I don't
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.94,0:14:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,have time for preamble. He said
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.74,0:14:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,the
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.91,0:14:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,cup down slowly on the saucer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.43,0:14:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The clink of porcelain was the
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.95,0:14:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,only sound at the table for a
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.42,0:14:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.33,0:14:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You owe $12,000 to the Costanza
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.36,0:14:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Brothers. He said. Neighborhood
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.40,0:14:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,loan-sharking. You lost your job
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.49,0:14:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,on Monday.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.67,0:14:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You lost your apartment on
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.10,0:14:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Wednesday. You have a friend who
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.87,0:14:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,offered you her couch. You have
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.58,0:14:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,no
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.69,0:14:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,living relatives and providence.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.98,0:14:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And the fiancee? Enough. I cut
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.13,0:15:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,in. You've made your point. He
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.28,0:15:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.39,0:15:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Tilted his head a fraction of a
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.90,0:15:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,millimeter. In a gesture that
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.32,0:15:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,was almost a thank you for
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.59,0:15:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,my frankness. I was going to say
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.70,0:15:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,he continued that the fiancee is
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.82,0:15:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,a matter you still don't
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.40,0:15:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,understand,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.73,0:15:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,but today isn't the day for that
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.47,0:15:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,conversation. And what day is
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.05,0:15:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,that conversation? A day that
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.63,0:15:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,depends on what you do in the
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.20,0:15:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,next five minutes. The waiter
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.77,0:15:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,returned with my coffee. I took
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.44,0:15:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,a sip too
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.93,0:15:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,quickly and burned my tongue on
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.00,0:15:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,purpose to have a physical
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.73,0:15:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,reason to pay attention. Then
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.67,0:15:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,say it. I said,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.67,0:15:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Ludovico rested his elbow on the
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.80,0:15:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,table. The old watch gleamed in
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.87,0:15:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,the low light. I erase every
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.73,0:15:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,cent of your debt. I buy the
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.35,0:15:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Costanza's papers tonight. I
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.96,0:15:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,give you back the apartment if
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.69,0:15:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,you want,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.35,0:15:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,or arrange another one. I handle
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.28,0:15:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,the school problem. Mrs. Peretti
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.20,0:15:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,will get a phone call and
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.71,0:15:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,remember that she likes you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.30,0:15:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You're describing a miracle. I'm
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.13,0:15:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,describing a transaction.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.25,0:15:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides didn't waver. In
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.82,0:15:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,exchange for a single thing. I
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.79,0:15:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,took another sip. I didn't let
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.75,0:15:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,my hand
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.85,0:16:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,go. What thing? You marry me. On
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.08,0:16:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,paper. The cafe kept making
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.96,0:16:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,coffee around me. The steam wand
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.19,0:16:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,cut through the air. Someone
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.70,0:16:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,laughed at a distant table. And
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.37,0:16:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I sat there listening to the
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.87,0:16:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,most
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.09,0:16:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,feared man in Providence
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.21,0:16:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,offering me a contract marriage
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.65,0:16:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,with the same calm you'd order
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.04,0:16:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,the check.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.97,0:16:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that a marriage proposal? I
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.09,0:16:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,said slowly, or a purchase
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.94,0:16:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,order. He almost smiled. Again,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.55,0:16:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,he didn't smile. It's a
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.01,0:16:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,proposal. You can refuse. You
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.84,0:16:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,can get up from this table right
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.87,0:16:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,now. And the
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.63,0:16:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,only thing I'll do is pay for
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.28,0:16:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,your coffee. And tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.76,0:16:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow the Costanza brothers
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.47,0:16:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,still exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.67,0:16:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And the eviction notice is still
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.27,0:16:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,taped to the door. I held the
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.71,0:16:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,cup more firmly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.21,0:16:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Marriage on paper. I repeated.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.19,0:16:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What does that mean exactly? A
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.18,0:16:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,civil contract.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.87,0:16:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,City Hall. No religious
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.23,0:16:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,ceremony. He began counting the
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.07,0:16:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,rules on his fingers.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.83,0:16:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Without lifting his hand from
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.44,0:16:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,the table. Just moving them one
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.16,0:16:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,by one. You live in my house.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.77,0:16:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You have your own room. I have
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.86,0:16:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,another. Both doors stay closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.10,0:16:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on. In public, you're my
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.98,0:17:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.65,0:17:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You go to events with me. You
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.40,0:17:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,smile when it's time to smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.21,0:17:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't need to pretend more
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.03,0:17:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.83,0:17:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,In private, nothing. I won't
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.71,0:17:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,touch you. I won't go into your
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.79,0:17:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,room. I won't ask about your
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.67,0:17:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,life.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.39,0:17:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And you won't ask about mine. No
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.51,0:17:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,questions. No questions. I set
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.49,0:17:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,the cup on the saucer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.95,0:17:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought that no questions had
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.76,0:17:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,the smell of a locked door. And
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.56,0:17:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,locked doors were exactly the
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.25,0:17:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,ones I always wanted to open.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.15,0:17:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,For how long? One year. After
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.04,0:17:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,that, you can ask for the
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.68,0:17:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,separation
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.33,0:17:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,without any contest from me. If
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.20,0:17:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,you'd rather stay longer, it's
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.00,0:17:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,negotiable. Why me? It was the
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.81,0:17:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,first
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.11,0:17:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,question of mine that took him a
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.96,0:17:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,second longer to answer. Just a
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.75,0:17:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,second. Because you need it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.57,0:17:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,His voice dropped half a tone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.17,0:17:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And because I need a wife for
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.72,0:17:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,reasons that don't fit into this
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.43,0:17:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,conversation, I held his gaze.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.36,0:17:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,He held mine. Neither of us
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.10,0:17:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,blinked for a stretch of time
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.97,0:17:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,that
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.23,0:17:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,would have been awkward at any
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.82,0:17:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,other table. I'll think about
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.36,0:17:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,it. I said, you haven't till
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.85,0:17:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,tomorrow morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.59,0:17:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Me. He took from the inner
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.88,0:18:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,pocket of his jacket, a
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.01,0:18:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,cream-colored card with tall,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.45,0:18:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,firm handwriting.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.79,0:18:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The address of a city hall. If
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.93,0:18:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,you show up, it's yes. If you
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.99,0:18:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,don't, it's no. I took the card.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.75,0:18:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Our fingers didn't touch, but
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.19,0:18:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,they passed so close that I felt
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.78,0:18:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,the warmth of his hand for
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.07,0:18:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,a second before I pulled mine
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.02,0:18:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,back. Do you always negotiate
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.97,0:18:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,like this? I asked two sentences
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.12,0:18:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,in a card?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.27,0:18:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,No. He leaned back in his chair.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.13,0:18:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But with you, I didn't want to
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.88,0:18:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,make things up. I stood up from
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.69,0:18:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,the table. I didn't thank him
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.41,0:18:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,for the coffee. He didn't expect
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.30,0:18:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,me to. I walked to the door with
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.19,0:18:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,my
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.31,0:18:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,backstrate, knowing all of
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.76,0:18:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Providence would be recounting
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.44,0:18:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,this scene for weeks. When I
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.01,0:18:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,touched the
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.62,0:18:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,handle, I heard behind me, low.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.25,0:18:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Almost thought aloud. Two sugar
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.89,0:18:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,cubes, a drop of milk.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.32,0:18:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I stopped. I looked over my
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.98,0:18:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,shoulder. What? Ludovico didn't
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.88,0:18:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,look at me. He was stirring his
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.79,0:18:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,own coffee
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.40,0:18:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,with a small spoon. That's how
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.16,0:18:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,you take it. When you're not
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.81,0:18:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,testing me, I stood there a
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.40,0:18:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,second longer
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.16,0:19:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,than I should have. Then I
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.35,0:19:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,opened the door and left. I
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.63,0:19:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,slept badly. I woke before the
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.16,0:19:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.50,0:19:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I shoured. Put on the least
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.17,0:19:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,wrinkled blue dress in my
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.71,0:19:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,closet. Gathered my documents
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.50,0:19:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,into a small
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.24,0:19:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,bag and went down the stairs
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.90,0:19:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,without saying goodbye to a
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.50,0:19:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,single thing. I left a short
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.16,0:19:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,note
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.40,0:19:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,for Narina on the kitchen table.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.17,0:19:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The kind that explains nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.84,0:19:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,and promises everything. I'd
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.39,0:19:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,have to
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.78,0:19:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,take the scolding later. City
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.50,0:19:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Hall was three blocks from the
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.27,0:19:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,harbor. I arrived 15 minutes
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.93,0:19:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,before
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.28,0:19:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,nine. He was already there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.03,0:19:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Leaning against the corridor
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.84,0:19:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,wall. Hands in his jacket
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.46,0:19:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,pockets.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.98,0:19:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Looking at his own shoe like
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.36,0:19:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,someone who'd been waiting long
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.90,0:19:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,enough to have memorized the
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.28,0:19:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.08,0:19:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Beside him, an older man, broad
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.94,0:19:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,shouldered, but the look of
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.56,0:19:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,someone who'd come back from
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.24,0:19:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,wars no one had named. Ludovico
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.20,0:19:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,raised his head when he saw me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.16,0:19:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't smile. He made no
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.87,0:19:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.12,0:19:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,He just waited for me to arrive.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.26,0:19:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning. I said, good
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.99,0:19:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,morning. He made a discrete
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.79,0:19:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,gesture
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.26,0:19:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,toward the man beside him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.90,0:19:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Bastion del Rose. He works with
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.85,0:20:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,me. He'll be nearby whenever you
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.86,0:20:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,go out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.30,0:20:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Bastion tilted his head half a
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.54,0:20:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,degree. No hello, no pleasure,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.78,0:20:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,no smile, just the half degree.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.66,0:20:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you. I answered
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.24,0:20:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,anyway because my grandmother
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.87,0:20:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,would have smacked me if I
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.33,0:20:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,didn't answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.66,0:20:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The clerk called us. We went
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.27,0:20:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,into a small room with a long
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.94,0:20:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,table.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.80,0:20:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Papers already prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.06,0:20:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Ludovico pushed them toward me
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.64,0:20:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,before the clerk could open his
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.26,0:20:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.02,0:20:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Read it. Slowly. If there's any
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.21,0:20:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,claws you don't accept, we redo
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.40,0:20:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,it. I read every line.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.96,0:20:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It was exactly the way he'd said
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.02,0:20:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,in the cafe. Separate rooms,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.50,0:20:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,appearances in public, no
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.45,0:20:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,questions, one year, right of
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.70,0:20:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,unilateral exit on her part. I
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.04,0:20:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,reached the last page and slid
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.56,0:20:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,my finger down to the signature
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.13,0:20:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,line. I saw nothing I wasn't
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.55,0:20:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,supposed
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.96,0:20:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,to see. Not then. It's fine. I
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.54,0:20:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,said, I signed. He signed after
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.21,0:20:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,me. The clerk stamped it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.60,0:20:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,There was no kiss, no photo, no
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.64,0:20:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,rice thrown on the way out. The
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.67,0:21:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,three of us left city hall in
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.18,0:21:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,the car was waiting. Black,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.23,0:21:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,glossy, glass-to-dark. The kind
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.59,0:21:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,my father used to tell me not to
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.02,0:21:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,look at when I was a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.58,0:21:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Bestion opened the rear door.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.27,0:21:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Ludovico got in from the other
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.00,0:21:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,side and sat
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.70,0:21:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,next to me without saying
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.97,0:21:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,anything. The car took the road
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.56,0:21:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,toward the upper suburb.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.32,0:21:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Providence shrank in the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.17,0:21:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The red rooftops falling away
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.85,0:21:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,behind us. In green took over.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.00,0:21:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't speak the entire way.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.80,0:21:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Neither did I. The mansion gate
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.61,0:21:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,appeared after 20 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.12,0:21:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Dark iron, tall, with a discreet
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.39,0:21:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,crest in the center. A lion's
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.45,0:21:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,head with the crown split in
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.44,0:21:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,two.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.02,0:21:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't ask what it meant. It
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.85,0:21:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,was part of the no questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.61,0:21:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The gate opened. The car went up
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.56,0:21:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,a
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.62,0:21:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,lane of low trees. I saw the
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.32,0:21:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,house before I knew it was a
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.02,0:21:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,house. Three stories of pale
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.72,0:21:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,stone,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.48,0:21:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,tall windows, a double staircase
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.64,0:21:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,at the entrance. A small woman,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.72,0:21:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,my grandmother's age,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.14,0:21:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,appeared at the door above. Her
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.42,0:21:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,pulled into a low bun, white
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.49,0:21:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,apron, dry hands,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.44,0:22:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,donachyata, Ludovico said, this
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.64,0:22:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,is Yolanda. Donachyata looked me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.92,0:22:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,over from head to toe,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.86,0:22:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,not with judgment, with concern.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.70,0:22:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The kind of look only a kitchen
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.48,0:22:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,woman knows how to give.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.30,0:22:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome. She said, you must be
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.39,0:22:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,tired. I'm fine. She didn't
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.27,0:22:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,believe me, but she nodded and
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.36,0:22:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,didn't
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.78,0:22:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,insist. Ludovico took me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.36,0:22:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,upstairs. The upper corridor was
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.47,0:22:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,long, with identical door
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.12,0:22:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,as on both sides. He stopped at
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.86,0:22:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,the third door on the right and
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.59,0:22:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,opened it. This is your room.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.56,0:22:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It was too big for one person. A
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.80,0:22:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,canopy double bed, a desk at the
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.03,0:22:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,window, a built-in closet
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.78,0:22:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,along an entire wall. Everything
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.93,0:22:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,in shades of cream and gray, a
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.95,0:22:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,tasteful cold. My room is at the
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.10,0:22:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,end
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.30,0:22:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,of the corridor. He said, behind
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.23,0:22:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,me, on the left side, you don't
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.09,0:22:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,need to go past it. Understood?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.96,0:22:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,If you need anything, Donachyata
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.59,0:22:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,is always nearby. And you, he
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.97,0:22:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,paused a second. If you need me,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.92,0:22:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Donachyata knows where I am. I
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.47,0:22:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,turned to look at him. He was
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.98,0:22:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,standing in the doorway,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.74,0:23:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,one hand on the handle, looking
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.32,0:23:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,at some point between my
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.54,0:23:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,shoulder and the window. For the
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.17,0:23:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,first time
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.68,0:23:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,since the cafe, he seemed unsure
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.83,0:23:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,of where to put his gaze. Thank
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.91,0:23:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,you. I said, I wasn't quite sure
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.06,0:23:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,why. He tilted his head a
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.61,0:23:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,fraction of a millimeter. Close
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.53,0:23:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,the door. I heard his footsteps
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.46,0:23:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,go
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.58,0:23:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,down the corridor, in silence. I
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.55,0:23:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,sat on the edge of the bed. I
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.34,0:23:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,ran my hand over the dovet,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.38,0:23:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and the fabric was soft in a way
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.06,0:23:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,that made my eyes sting without
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.69,0:23:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,warning. I didn't cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.36,0:23:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Not that first afternoon. That
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.32,0:23:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,night, Donachyata came up with a
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.42,0:23:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,tray, hot soup,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.72,0:23:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,fresh bread, a glass of red
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.35,0:23:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,wine. I didn't ask her to swap
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.15,0:23:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,it for water. I drank the wine
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.96,0:23:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,to the
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.32,0:23:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,last drop. I lay down without
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.76,0:23:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,changing my clothes and stared
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.26,0:23:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,at the ceiling of the canopy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.70,0:23:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Near midnight, I heard footsteps
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.02,0:23:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,in the corridor, slow, measured
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.26,0:23:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,footsteps. They came from the
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.36,0:23:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,end of the corridor. They
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.72,0:23:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,reached my door. They stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.35,0:23:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,They stood there for a stretch
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.98,0:23:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,of time. I
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.52,0:23:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,couldn't measure. Five seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.86,0:23:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Ten. More than ten. He didn't
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.06,0:24:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,knock. He didn't call out. He
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.25,0:24:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,made no
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.78,0:24:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,sound. Then the footsteps went
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.65,0:24:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,back. I heard them move away
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.39,0:24:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,slowly. The same rhythm in the
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.26,0:24:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,direction
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.82,0:24:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,they had come from. The door at
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.68,0:24:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,the end of the corridor opened.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.54,0:24:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Closed. I stared at the canopy
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.34,0:24:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,in the
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.70,0:24:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,same position and understood,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.49,0:24:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,lying in that bed too big for
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.28,0:24:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,one person, that the man the
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.00,0:24:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,town feared
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.68,0:24:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,had come to my door on the first
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.84,0:24:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,night. Not to come in, not to
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.81,0:24:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,speak. Only to stop outside,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.16,0:24:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,and then go back. I closed my
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.31,0:24:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,eyes. I didn't sleep. The
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.17,0:24:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Karatio Lomanshin woke before I
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.47,0:24:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,did. I
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.92,0:24:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,discovered this on the first
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.22,0:24:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,morning when I came down the
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.51,0:24:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,marble stairs still in my robe
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.90,0:24:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,fastened up to my neck and found
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.83,0:24:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,the house already breathing.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.52,0:24:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Donachiyara, tidying the
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.97,0:24:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,sideboard in the
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.94,0:24:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,hall, the smell of fresh bread
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.53,0:24:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,coming from the kitchen. A staff
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.22,0:24:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,member I didn't recognize
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.54,0:24:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,cleaning
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.96,0:24:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,the vestibule stained glass with
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.66,0:24:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,silent movements. No one looked
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.31,0:24:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,at me as if I didn't belong
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.74,0:24:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,there.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.44,0:24:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,No one looked at me as if I
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.87,0:24:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,belonged either. It was worse
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.41,0:24:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,than hostility. It was
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.58,0:24:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,professional
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.22,0:25:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,neutrality. Good morning, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.28,0:25:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Donachiyara said, seeing me
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.02,0:25:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,standing in the kitchen archway.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.08,0:25:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Coffee here or in the garden
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.79,0:25:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,room, it took me a second to
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.50,0:25:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,understand that ma'am was me.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.27,0:25:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Here is fine,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.46,0:25:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I answered. If it's not in the
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.26,0:25:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,way, she laughed softly. The
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.94,0:25:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,kind of laugh only Italian women
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.86,0:25:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,of a certain
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.58,0:25:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,age know how to give without
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.07,0:25:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,taking their hands off their
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.56,0:25:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,apron. You, in the way in my
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.05,0:25:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,kitchen,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.08,0:25:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,that's a good one. I sat on the
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.74,0:25:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,wooden bench against the
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.03,0:25:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,counter. Donachiyara said a cup
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.69,0:25:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,in front of
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.28,0:25:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,me without asking how I wanted
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.95,0:25:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,it. Two sugar cubes had been
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.50,0:25:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,dissolved in it. A drop of milk
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.22,0:25:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,had been added on top. The
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.71,0:25:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,coffee was exactly the color I'd
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.54,0:25:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,been drinking since I was 15.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.78,0:25:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I held the cup with both hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.61,0:25:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you tell Mr. Ludovico?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.14,0:25:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Donachiyara kept stirring a pot
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.97,0:25:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,on the
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.32,0:25:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,stove without turning around. No
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.25,0:25:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,one needed to tell me anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.11,0:25:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,my dear. Mr. Ludovico left it
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.86,0:25:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,noted.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.52,0:25:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,He asked that it be this way
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.26,0:25:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,every day. She paused briefly.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.12,0:25:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Always. I drank the coffee too
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.99,0:25:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,slowly.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.00,0:25:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That was how the first week
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.56,0:25:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,went. I'd discover a house rule
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.36,0:26:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,by accident. And Ludovico had
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.03,0:26:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,already
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.44,0:26:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,altered the rule in silence so
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.29,0:26:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd fit inside it. On Monday, I
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.21,0:26:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,mentioned aloud to Donachiyara
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.06,0:26:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,that I missed the bookside left
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.82,0:26:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,in my apartment. On Tuesday,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.42,0:26:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,three of my favorites were on
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.07,0:26:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,the
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.24,0:26:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,little table in my room with new
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.29,0:26:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,bookmarks between the pages. On
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.29,0:26:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Wednesday, I told Bastion I
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.02,0:26:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,hated
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.34,0:26:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,the black car because it
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.77,0:26:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,reminded me of a funeral. I only
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.67,0:26:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,said it sarcastically, because
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.46,0:26:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,he
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.58,0:26:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,appeared in a dark suit in the
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.23,0:26:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,corridor and I wanted to provoke
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.99,0:26:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,him. On Thursday, Bastion
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.36,0:26:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,appeared
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.80,0:26:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,at the winter garden door with
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.30,0:26:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,his hands folded in front of his
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.90,0:26:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,body, with the stone face that
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.40,0:26:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,was already his trademark. He
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.90,0:26:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,asked me to ask whether you'd
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.40,0:26:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,prefer the gray car or the black
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.05,0:26:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,one to
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.36,0:26:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,go out today. I looked up from
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.41,0:26:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,my book. Do I have something
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.33,0:26:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,scheduled today? You will, if
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.32,0:26:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,you want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.46,0:26:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,He blinked once. Bastion, I
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.20,0:26:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,said, trying not to laugh. Were
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.19,0:26:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,you always like this or were you
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.25,0:26:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,trained?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.32,0:26:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Both, ma'am. And he went back
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.85,0:26:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,down the corridor with a step
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.38,0:26:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,identical to the one he derived
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.02,0:26:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,with.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.28,0:26:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I kept staring at the door for
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.89,0:27:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,half a minute with the book
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.33,0:27:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,forgotten in my lap,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.88,0:27:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,and admitted to myself that this
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.34,0:27:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,house was starting to become an
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.75,0:27:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,intimate joke I had an asked to
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.17,0:27:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,be
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.26,0:27:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,part of. The problem was, the
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.15,0:27:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,joke had an owner, and the owner
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.23,0:27:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,of the joke didn't smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.62,0:27:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Ludovico and I crossed paths
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.51,0:27:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,with icy formality. In the
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.27,0:27:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,corridor, he'd nod,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.20,0:27:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,half a degree, enough not to be
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.17,0:27:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,rude. At dinner, we sat at the
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.08,0:27:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,two ends of the long table like
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.05,0:27:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,two
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.24,0:27:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,chest pieces pretending the
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.74,0:27:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,board was too big for any
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.12,0:27:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,attack. He'd ask if I'd needed
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.78,0:27:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.86,0:27:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd answer no. He'd ask if Dona
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.86,0:27:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Chiarra had been kind. I'd
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.55,0:27:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,answer that she was an angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.42,0:27:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,He'd
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.68,0:27:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,fold his napkin and stand up. No
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.66,0:27:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,questions. That was the rule. He
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.64,0:27:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,kept the rule better than I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.12,0:27:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Wednesday evening, Narina showed
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.55,0:27:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,up at the gate with a leather
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.84,0:27:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,bag that looked like it weighed
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.22,0:27:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,more than she did. Bastion
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.78,0:27:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,opened the gate for her without
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.64,0:27:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,arguing. Dona Chiarra hugged her
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.56,0:27:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,like
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.70,0:27:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Narina walked through the hall
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.31,0:27:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,with wide eyes and a comment on
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.97,0:27:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,the tip of her tongue. This
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.41,0:27:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,place
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.68,0:27:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,looks like a museum with
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.01,0:28:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,tasteful ghosts. I pulled her
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.62,0:28:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,into the kitchen before Ludovico
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.40,0:28:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,could
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.68,0:28:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,appear. Sweetie, she whispered,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.77,0:28:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,taking a Tupperware container
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.73,0:28:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,out of her bag. I brought my
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.62,0:28:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,grandmother's
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.50,0:28:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,lasagna, not that Dona Chiarra
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.28,0:28:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,needs help, but my grandma liked
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.18,0:28:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,you, and I wasn't going to let
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.96,0:28:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,that slide. You're a social
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.86,0:28:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,hazard. I know. Where does he
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.90,0:28:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,sleep? Narina? Just so I know
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.94,0:28:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,the distance
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.78,0:28:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,between the two rooms, Missy.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.70,0:28:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's field research. We sat on
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.68,0:28:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,the kitchen bench, split the
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.54,0:28:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,lasagna
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.00,0:28:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,into two bowls, and ate in
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.42,0:28:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,secret like two teenagers who'd
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.11,0:28:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,snuck out of the cafeteria.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.21,0:28:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It was the first time I'd
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.58,0:28:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,laughed since the church bell. I
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.34,0:28:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,laughed for real. My face half
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.99,0:28:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,lowered,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.13,0:28:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,almost choking on a piece of
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.02,0:28:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,cheese. Dona Chiarra passed by
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.04,0:28:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,the door, pretended not to see,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.39,0:28:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,and kept going toward the
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.83,0:28:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,garden. Ludovico passed by the
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.56,0:28:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,door five minutes later.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.95,0:28:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,He also pretended not to see,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.84,0:28:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,but I saw him. He had his shirts
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.94,0:29:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,leave rolled up to the elbow,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.25,0:29:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,his hair a little out of place.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.96,0:29:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The kind of detail I shouldn't
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.62,0:29:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,have registered. He stopped in
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.28,0:29:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,the
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.45,0:29:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,archway for half a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.95,0:29:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly long enough to identify
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.75,0:29:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,me laughing, and kept going down
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.60,0:29:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,the corridor
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.29,0:29:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,without saying anything. Narina
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.12,0:29:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,gave me a discreet kick on the
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.88,0:29:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,foot under the bench. Sweetie,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.03,0:29:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,she whispered, mouthful. That
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.50,0:29:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,man just looked at you the way
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.03,0:29:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,you look at an open window in
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.50,0:29:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,the middle
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.01,0:29:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,of winter. Shut up. It's a
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.74,0:29:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,professional observation. You're
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.87,0:29:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,a music teacher, Narina.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.17,0:29:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Music is observation, my girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.93,0:29:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think we listen to?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.76,0:29:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I nudged her with my elbow. She
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.58,0:29:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,laughed.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.59,0:29:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Dona Chiarra came back with a
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.03,0:29:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,picture of water as if nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.53,0:29:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,had happened. I took a long
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.87,0:29:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,sip and said nothing more. That
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.94,0:29:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,night, when Narina left, the
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.81,0:29:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,corridor was too silent. I
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.54,0:29:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,passed the
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.21,0:29:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,library door, and saw the light
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.28,0:29:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,on under the crack. I didn't go
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.36,0:29:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,in. I went to my room,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.83,0:29:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,closed the door, and took a long
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.78,0:29:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,time to fall asleep. The kitchen
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.74,0:29:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,was too big for crying at dawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.05,0:29:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I discovered this three days
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.70,0:30:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,later, on Monday, when I came
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.41,0:30:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,down barefoot at three in the
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.12,0:30:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.11,0:30:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,because I'd woken with my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.82,0:30:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,in my throat, and a dream of an
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.52,0:30:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,empty church stuck to my neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.59,0:30:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I turned on only the light above
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.37,0:30:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,the stove. I sat on the cold
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.92,0:30:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,floor with my back against the
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.59,0:30:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,cabinet.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.45,0:30:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The crying came without sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.12,0:30:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The way I'd learned to cry when
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.85,0:30:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I lived with my grandmother,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.41,0:30:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,and she didn't like to hear
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.14,0:30:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,sadness after ten at night. I
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.00,0:30:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,heard the footsteps before I saw
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.06,0:30:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,his
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.25,0:30:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,shadow in the archway. He didn't
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.91,0:30:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,turn on the main light. He stood
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.58,0:30:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,there for two seconds in the
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.03,0:30:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,doorway,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.05,0:30:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,in a white shirt open at the
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.69,0:30:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,collar. His hair sang he hadn't
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.52,0:30:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,slept either. He didn't ask
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.10,0:30:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.95,0:30:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I lifted my chin before he could
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.70,0:30:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,think of touching me. I don't
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.29,0:30:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,need an audience to cry. Thank
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.93,0:30:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,you.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.39,0:30:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,He stopped in a very specific
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.04,0:30:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,way, without retreating or
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.51,0:30:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,advancing. He just stayed.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.99,0:30:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, without saying a word, he
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.90,0:30:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,crossed the kitchen, opened the
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.81,0:30:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,cabinet beside my shoulder,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.01,0:30:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,and took out a glass. He filled
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.58,0:30:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,the glass with water at the
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.96,0:30:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,sink. He set the glass on the
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.43,0:30:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,floor near my
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.09,0:31:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,knee. He sat on the floor across
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.00,0:31:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,from me. His back against the
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.74,0:31:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,opposite cabinet, his legs
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.29,0:31:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,stretched
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.83,0:31:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,out in a way that made his feet
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.96,0:31:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,almost touch mine, and he
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.67,0:31:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,stayed. He didn't talk. He
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.46,0:31:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,didn't ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.67,0:31:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't offer a shoulder. He
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.63,0:31:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,stayed there. On the cold
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.26,0:31:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,kitchen floor, with his rumpled
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.28,0:31:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,shirt
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.61,0:31:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and his gaze on some point
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.26,0:31:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,between my knee and the
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.72,0:31:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,baseball, breathing slowly. I
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.56,0:31:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,cried for two
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.39,0:31:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,more minutes. I drank half the
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.51,0:31:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,glass. I cried a little more. I
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.71,0:31:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,drank the rest. When I stood up,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.27,0:31:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,he stood up too, without
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.72,0:31:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,touching me. He collected the
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.48,0:31:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,glass, carried it to the sink,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.83,0:31:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,washed it with the same calm he
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.61,0:31:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,did everything else. Good night,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.46,0:31:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Ayolanda. I went back to my room
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.30,0:31:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,and
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.47,0:31:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,took a long time to fall asleep
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.26,0:31:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,again, but for another reason,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.99,0:31:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,the first public dinner came on
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.78,0:31:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Friday night.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.61,0:31:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Il Jira Sole, a restaurant that
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.56,0:31:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,served all of Providence without
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.56,0:31:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,serving anyone properly,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.67,0:31:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,with a crystal chandelier and a
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.54,0:31:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,metre, who lowered his head half
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.46,0:31:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,a degree when Luda Vico entered.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.85,0:32:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,He told me at breakfast with a
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.58,0:32:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,short sentence. In the way I
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.20,0:32:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,already recognized as his way of
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.04,0:32:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,asking
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.39,0:32:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,without asking. Il Jira Sole,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.42,0:32:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,nine at night. It's important
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.45,0:32:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,that we appear together.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.69,0:32:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Dress? Whatever you think is
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.44,0:32:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,good, I chose the dark blue one,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.44,0:32:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,the one with thin straps that
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.25,0:32:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,held a mid-caf. I put on the
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.57,0:32:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,only pair of earrings I'd
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.76,0:32:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,brought from the old department.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.79,0:32:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I came down the stairs with my
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.36,0:32:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,hair pinned at the nape and saw
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.99,0:32:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Luda Vico waiting below,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.63,0:32:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,in a black suit that looked like
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.12,0:32:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,it had been cut on his body, and
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.61,0:32:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,an expression he managed to
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.87,0:32:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,keep closed for three seconds
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.29,0:32:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,before looking away.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.33,0:32:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go. He said. At the
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.43,0:32:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,restaurant, everyone looked. No
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.04,0:32:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,one stared.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.47,0:32:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,We sat at a table near the back.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.18,0:32:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The metre poured the wine with
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.78,0:32:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,slightly trembling hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.11,0:32:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Luda Vico ordered for me without
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.88,0:32:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,consulting me. A dish I wouldn't
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.65,0:32:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,have ordered,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.91,0:32:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,and that was exactly the way I
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.56,0:32:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,liked it. I raised an eyebrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.20,0:32:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Does Donut Jira have a notebook
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.90,0:32:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,of
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.01,0:32:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,records? I asked. She has a
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.80,0:32:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,memory. Her memory is about me,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.86,0:33:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,about everyone who sits at her
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.85,0:33:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,table.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.73,0:33:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I took a sip. Luda Vico. He
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.28,0:33:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,looked up. Does this still feel
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.06,0:33:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,more like a contract than a
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.61,0:33:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,marriage?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.61,0:33:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,He held the glass by the stem,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.26,0:33:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,swirled the wine a quarter turn,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.02,0:33:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,set the glass back on the table
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.73,0:33:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,without drinking. What would you
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.77,0:33:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,rather it feel like? I don't
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.55,0:33:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,know. I admitted. I'm still
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.27,0:33:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,figuring it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.67,0:33:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,He almost smiled. Almost. It was
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.65,0:33:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,at that moment that Renolfo
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.33,0:33:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Saravale crossed the restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.73,0:33:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know who he was. I only
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.42,0:33:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,felt the restaurant changed
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.85,0:33:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,temperature before he reached
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.38,0:33:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,the table.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.41,0:33:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Luda Vico stiffened half a
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.85,0:33:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,degree. Enough for me to notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.63,0:33:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Not enough for anyone else to
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.24,0:33:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.21,0:33:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Renolfo was a man in a light
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.90,0:33:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,suit, a wide smile and heavy
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.59,0:33:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,shoulders,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.19,0:33:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,with a colabrian accent that
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.98,0:33:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,dragged the consonants in a
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.70,0:33:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,strange way. Luda Vico,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.85,0:33:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,what a nice surprise. Renolfo.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.92,0:33:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And this must be the new Mrs.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.92,0:33:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Caracciolo. Renolfo turned to me
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.13,0:33:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,with theatrical courtesy and
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.75,0:33:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,extended his hand and immense
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.43,0:33:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,pleasure. Before I could decide
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.22,0:33:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,what to do with my hand,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.95,0:34:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Luda Vico simply looked at him.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.96,0:34:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't speak. He didn't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.03,0:34:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,He just looked. The look
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.59,0:34:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,lasted exactly the length of one
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.49,0:34:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,breath and Renolfo understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.27,0:34:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,He withdrew his hand with the
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.99,0:34:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,mile still hanging on his face,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.70,0:34:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,in the way of a man who knows
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.31,0:34:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,he's lost this round,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.91,0:34:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,and that the next subject is
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.63,0:34:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,better left untouched. Anyway,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.47,0:34:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Renolfo said with forced
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.95,0:34:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,lightness, good to see you Luda
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.97,0:34:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Vico. And good night, ma'am. He
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.98,0:34:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,left. I kept looking at Luda
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.80,0:34:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Vico.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.65,0:34:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,He went back to his glass
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.04,0:34:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,without comment. I didn't ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.72,0:34:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd learned quickly in that
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.22,0:34:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.17,0:34:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That asking about a scene like
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.71,0:34:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,that was a waste. It rained as
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.25,0:34:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,we left the restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.43,0:34:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Not a heavy rain. A fine rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.62,0:34:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Early autumn weather and
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.37,0:34:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,providence. The kind of rain
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.42,0:34:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,that
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.71,0:34:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,soaks you inside without seeming
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.46,0:34:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,to soak you. I'd forgotten a
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.99,0:34:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,coat. Luda Vico had already
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.47,0:34:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,opened the car door for me when
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.16,0:34:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,he noticed. Without saying a
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.68,0:34:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,word, he took off his own coat
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.31,0:34:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,from his shoulders and put it
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.90,0:34:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,over mine. The fabric was warm
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.54,0:34:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,from his body. It smelled of
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.07,0:34:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,something woody I couldn't name.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.82,0:35:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,He got in the car on the
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.14,0:35:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,driver's side. Bastion drove in
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.83,0:35:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,silence.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.27,0:35:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The way back to the mansion was
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.12,0:35:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,short. The coat weighed on my
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.86,0:35:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,back in a specific way.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.49,0:35:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,No one said anything. When
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.20,0:35:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Bastion parked, Luda Vico got
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.10,0:35:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,out, opened my door,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.85,0:35:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,and waited for me to step out.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.41,0:35:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,He still said nothing. He just
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.96,0:35:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,stood there on the gravel,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.81,0:35:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,with the fine rain wetting his
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.28,0:35:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,shirt, waiting for me to pass in
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.84,0:35:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,front so he could close the
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.17,0:35:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,door.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.63,0:35:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I climbed the entrance stairs
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.08,0:35:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,with his coat on my shoulders.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.57,0:35:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Bastion stayed down below.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.87,0:35:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,In the upper corridor, I
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.54,0:35:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,stopped. Luda Vico stopped two
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.63,0:35:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,steps behind. I took his coat
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.65,0:35:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,off my
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.07,0:35:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,shoulders very carefully. I held
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.91,0:35:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,it back out to him without fully
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.75,0:35:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,raising my eyes. Good night Luda
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.58,0:35:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Vico.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.43,0:35:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,He took the coat by the
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.55,0:35:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,shoulders. His thumb lingering a
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.11,0:35:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,second longer than it needed on
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.62,0:35:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,the
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.77,0:35:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,fabric that had touched my
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.36,0:35:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,shoulders. Good night, Ayolanda.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.32,0:35:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I went into my room. I closed
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.10,0:35:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.07,0:35:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I leaned my back against the
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.48,0:35:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,wood. I looked at the imaginary
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.03,0:35:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,coat I was no longer wearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.49,0:35:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,At the sensation of weight that
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.48,0:35:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,was still there, stubborn on my
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.46,0:36:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,shoulders. I put my hand to the
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.45,0:36:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,collar of my dress and felt my
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.17,0:36:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,own pulse at my fingertips,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.71,0:36:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,beating faster than it should.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.43,0:36:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That was
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.89,0:36:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,when I understood. It wasn't
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.55,0:36:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,fear of him. It never had been.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.39,0:36:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It was fear of what was
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.76,0:36:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,beginning
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.29,0:36:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,to move inside me every time he
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.14,0:36:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,stayed quiet in the right place,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.04,0:36:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,in the right way, at the right
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.83,0:36:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,time.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.49,0:36:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Fear of looking at a coat
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.64,0:36:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,hanging on a stranger's arm and
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.06,0:36:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,thinking of a woody scent.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.25,0:36:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Fear of the coffee served
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.64,0:36:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,exactly the way I'd been
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.98,0:36:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,drinking it since I was 15,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.11,0:36:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,without ever having told him.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.50,0:36:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Fear of having cried on the
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.80,0:36:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,kitchen floor with a man sitting
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.33,0:36:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,silently across from me and
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.17,0:36:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,discovering that for two
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.81,0:36:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,minutes, it was less lonely than
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.99,0:36:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,any
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.19,0:36:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,conversation I'd had in the last
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.13,0:36:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,ten years. I leaned my forehead
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.01,0:36:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,against the door. The bell had
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.83,0:36:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,told for the last time two weeks
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.68,0:36:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,ago. And on the wrong side of
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.36,0:36:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,the corridor, a man I'd signed a
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.21,0:36:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,track not to love was closing
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.93,0:36:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,his bedroom door in silence. At
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.77,0:36:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,the end of the same night, he'd
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.61,0:36:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,covered me with his coat in the
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.29,0:36:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,rain. That was where, with my
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.86,0:36:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,hands still on the handle and my
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.59,0:37:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,pulse beating at my collar, I
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.40,0:37:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,realized I was, for the first
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.21,0:37:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,time since the church, truly
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.95,0:37:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,afraid,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.91,0:37:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,and the fear had nothing to do
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.87,0:37:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,with death. Two
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.35,0:37:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,weeks later, I learned that a
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.97,0:37:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,mansion sleeps
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.75,0:37:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,differently from normal houses.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.58,0:37:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't sleep actually. It
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.30,0:37:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,slows down. The night staff
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.89,0:37:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,moved
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.19,0:37:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,through the corridors and silent
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.87,0:37:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,shoes. The lighting recedes to a
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.56,0:37:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,series of dim sconces along the
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.19,0:37:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,baseboard. And the vestibules
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.75,0:37:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,old clocks keep marking time as
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.42,0:37:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,if no one had asked their
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.76,0:37:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,opinion.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.69,0:37:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I had grown used to crossing
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.20,0:37:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,that silence barefoot. In my
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.72,0:37:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,robe fastened up to my neck,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.55,0:37:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,when I couldn't sleep. And less
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.60,0:37:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,and less could I sleep. That
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.44,0:37:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Monday dawn, I went down to get
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.49,0:37:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,a glass
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.95,0:37:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,of water. That was the official
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.81,0:37:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,excuse. The real one I wouldn't
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.67,0:37:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,have the courage to admit,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.23,0:37:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,even to myself. The library
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.04,0:37:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,light was on. A yellow band
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.85,0:37:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,escaped from beneath the
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.46,0:37:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,half-open door.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.95,0:37:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I stopped in the corridor with
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.71,0:37:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,my hand at the waist of my robe.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.59,0:37:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I could go back. I should go
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.24,0:37:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,back.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.93,0:38:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I went forward. I pushed the
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.65,0:38:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,door with two fingers. Ludovico
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.54,0:38:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,was sitting in the tall armchair
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.50,0:38:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,near
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.75,0:38:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,the fireplace. His elbows on his
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.08,0:38:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,knees, and an untouched glass of
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.41,0:38:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,amber in his hand. No tie. No
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.52,0:38:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,jacket.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.03,0:38:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,His white shirt open at the
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.38,0:38:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,collar and the sleeves rolled up
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.97,0:38:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,to the elbow the way he did when
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.57,0:38:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,he
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.67,0:38:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,worked outside the office. The
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.48,0:38:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,fire was low. The orange light
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.30,0:38:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,ran across his face and revealed
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.23,0:38:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,what
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.47,0:38:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,the day's mask hid. The short
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.14,0:38:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,scar at his temple that I'd
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.70,0:38:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,never noticed. The weariness in
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.48,0:38:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,his shoulders.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.03,0:38:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The jaw clenched in the way of
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.75,0:38:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,someone carrying something for
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.46,0:38:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,far too long. He raised his
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.00,0:38:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.63,0:38:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,He wasn't startled. Couldn't
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.42,0:38:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,sleep. I came for water. The
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.22,0:38:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,kitchens on the other side.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.95,0:38:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I fastened the robe a little
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.51,0:38:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,tighter at my neck. You couldn't
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.29,0:38:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,either. He turned the glass
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.79,0:38:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,slowly between his fingers. I
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.72,0:38:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,don't drink. He said, looking at
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.84,0:38:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,the amber. I just hold it.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.83,0:38:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? Because if I drink, I talk
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.16,0:38:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,too much. We fell silent. I
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.18,0:38:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,shouldn't go in. I went in.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.63,0:39:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I sat in the armchair across
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.25,0:39:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,from his. With my legs folded to
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.10,0:39:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,the side. And the robe pulled
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.78,0:39:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,over my knees.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.15,0:39:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Neither of us moved for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.84,0:39:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The fire crackled. One of the
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.36,0:39:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,corridor clock struck three in
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.95,0:39:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,the distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.95,0:39:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,My brother liked this library.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.89,0:39:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,He said suddenly. As if
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.38,0:39:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,continuing a conversation we'd
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.33,0:39:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,never
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.65,0:39:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,started. He'd read lying there.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.55,0:39:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,On the rug, he said our father's
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.51,0:39:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,chair was uncomfortable on
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.10,0:39:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.13,0:39:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,So no one would think of staying
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.21,0:39:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,too long. I didn't ask the name.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.28,0:39:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I waited. In Rico.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.99,0:39:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Ludovico kept looking at the
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.63,0:39:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,glass. He was 19 when the set of
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.51,0:39:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,olives sent a message in an
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.10,0:39:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,alley
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.39,0:39:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,in the old district. I was 22.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.54,0:39:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,My father still alive. I was
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.54,0:39:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,forced to wait six years before
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.76,0:39:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.83,0:39:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,could collect that debt. I got
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.79,0:39:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,to the alley late. I got there
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.75,0:39:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,on time with Rinalpho. A log
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.57,0:39:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,shifted
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.03,0:39:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,in the fireplace and sent a
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.73,0:39:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,small spark toward the rug. He
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.62,0:39:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,looked at the spark with the
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.38,0:39:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,same calm
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.95,0:39:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,he looked at everything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.81,0:39:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The spark went out on its own.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.74,0:39:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I said, and the
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.42,0:39:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,sentence
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.93,0:40:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,came out low. Without ornament.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.12,0:40:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,He nodded. Half a degree. That
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.24,0:40:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,was all. I leaned my forehead
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.29,0:40:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,against the back of the
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.63,0:40:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,armchair. Without planning to, I
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.50,0:40:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,started to talk. My mother ran
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.26,0:40:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,away
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.49,0:40:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,from home when I was seven. I
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.37,0:40:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,said, with a man in debt. My
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.19,0:40:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,grandmother never forgave her.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.14,0:40:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,She raised
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.79,0:40:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,me saying that owing someone was
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.43,0:40:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,the same as owing yourself, and
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.02,0:40:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,that a woman who depends on
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.41,0:40:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,others pays with her body sooner
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.39,0:40:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,or later. I swore from the age
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.25,0:40:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,of ten that I would never owe
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.05,0:40:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,anyone anything. I raised my
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.61,0:40:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,eyes to him. He was watching me
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.35,0:40:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,with an attention that had
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.80,0:40:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.19,0:40:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,to do with negotiation. Then I
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.00,0:40:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,sat down across from a man in a
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.86,0:40:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,cafe and signed a contract.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.49,0:40:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I finished. My grandmother would
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.61,0:40:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,laugh in my face. Lutavico
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.32,0:40:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,turned the glass once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.49,0:40:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't owe anyone anything I
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.81,0:40:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,alanda. I owe $12,000 to
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.61,0:40:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,someone. You no longer do. Then
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.94,0:40:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I owe
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.31,0:40:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,$12,000 to you. He leaned half a
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.58,0:40:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,degree forward. His elbows still
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.85,0:40:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,resting on his knees. No.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.21,0:40:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,No? You owe me exactly what I
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.28,0:41:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,wrote in the contract. Not one
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.42,0:41:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,comma more. Silence. We stayed
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.55,0:41:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,there
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.91,0:41:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,for another stretch of time. I
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.40,0:41:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,couldn't measure. Neither of us
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.94,0:41:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,touched the other. Neither of us
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.53,0:41:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,said anything else of
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.83,0:41:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,importance, but something moved
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.75,0:41:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,beneath my ribcage. Something
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.55,0:41:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,warm, uncomfortable,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.55,0:41:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,that I had come to the library
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.17,0:41:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,terrified of finding. I stood up
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.89,0:41:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,before it became impossible to
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.51,0:41:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.35,0:41:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Good night, Lutavico. Good
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.17,0:41:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,night, Eolanda. I went to my
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.12,0:41:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,room. I didn't sleep. But this
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.22,0:41:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,time,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.63,0:41:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,the reason was different.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.05,0:41:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Tuesday afternoon I made the
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.65,0:41:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,mistake I'd been putting off
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.24,0:41:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,making. The door
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.15,0:41:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,to the small back room next to
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.95,0:41:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Lutavico's main office stayed
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.69,0:41:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,locked. I'd noticed this in the
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.55,0:41:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,second
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.91,0:41:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,week. That afternoon, passing
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.87,0:41:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,through the corridor, I noticed
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.96,0:41:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,the door was a jar, not locked.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.57,0:41:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Dona Ciara had a headache and
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.12,0:41:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Bastion had gone out with
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.45,0:41:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Lutavico to someplace no one
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.94,0:41:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,told me about.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.87,0:41:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I went in. I should have left
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.61,0:41:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,the same second. I didn't leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.53,0:41:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The small room was a smaller
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.21,0:41:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,office, full of files, steel
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.34,0:42:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,shelves, a side table, an open
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.61,0:42:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,folder left on the table,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.51,0:42:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,forgotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.97,0:42:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I went to the table as if my
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.50,0:42:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,body had gone before my head. I
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.20,0:42:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,lifted the folder cover. The
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.74,0:42:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,first
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.01,0:42:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,paper was a photo. A delmo.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.73,0:42:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,thinner than the last time I'd
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.65,0:42:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,seen him. With a poorly shaved
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.57,0:42:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,beard,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.51,0:42:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,coming out of a building that
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.11,0:42:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,wasn't in Providence. The photo
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.82,0:42:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,had a date at the bottom. Two
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.41,0:42:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,weeks
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.69,0:42:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,after the church bell. beneath
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.50,0:42:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,the photo, an address in Newark,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.44,0:42:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,New Jersey. beneath the address,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.91,0:42:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,an envelope with handwritten
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.41,0:42:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,notes and a firm slanted script.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.12,0:42:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The same as the note that had
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.68,0:42:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,arrived
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.05,0:42:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,at my apartment. Is a delmo.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.33,0:42:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Transfer confirmed. Silence paid
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.94,0:42:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,until further notice. I read it
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.46,0:42:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,three
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.87,0:42:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,times. I didn't understand. I
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.76,0:42:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,read it twice more. I understood
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.85,0:42:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,too little. That was when I
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.61,0:42:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,noticed
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.07,0:42:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,the step behind me. I turned
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.83,0:42:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,slowly. Ludovico was in the
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.53,0:42:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,doorway. He didn't huff. He
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.22,0:42:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,didn't raise his voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.17,0:42:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,He just looked at the folder in
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.88,0:42:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,my hand than it me. Closed that
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.60,0:42:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,door behind you when you leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.31,0:42:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,He said,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.99,0:43:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,he didn't say to close it from
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.61,0:43:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,the inside. He said to close it
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.28,0:43:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,from the outside. I dropped the
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.95,0:43:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,folder on the table. My heart
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.75,0:43:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,beating in some spot that wasn't
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.73,0:43:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,my chest. I left. I passed by
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.52,0:43:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,him
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.71,0:43:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,without looking. I went to the
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.31,0:43:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,corridor. I was already crying
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.91,0:43:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,by the middle of the stairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.41,0:43:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Angry at the crying. Angry are
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.33,0:43:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,still at what I was feeling
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.05,0:43:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,beneath the crying. Over the
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.84,0:43:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,next few
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.35,0:43:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,hours, I rehearsed in my head
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.93,0:43:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,three different versions of the
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.62,0:43:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,same sentence. You knew where he
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.36,0:43:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,was from the
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.01,0:43:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,start. I knocked on the main
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.23,0:43:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,office door two hours later. He
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.68,0:43:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,told me to come in. He was
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.74,0:43:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,standing, hands
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.93,0:43:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,on the back of the chair,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.97,0:43:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,waiting. As if he knew. You knew
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.58,0:43:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,where he was. I said, I
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.45,0:43:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,knew. Since when.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.57,0:43:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Since before you walked into the
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.49,0:43:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,cafe, what does that mean? He
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.23,0:43:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,didn't answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.69,0:43:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Ludovico, Yolanda. What does
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.50,0:43:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,that mean? He let the air out
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.37,0:43:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,through his nose. He didn't
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.12,0:43:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,answer properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.73,0:43:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,He just looked at me in a way I
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.50,0:43:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,couldn't read. I knew his
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.93,0:43:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,silence now. I'd learn to read
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.64,0:43:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,many
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.87,0:44:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,silences in that house, but this
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.86,0:44:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,was a new silence. It wasn't the
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.84,0:44:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,silence of the rule. It was the
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.77,0:44:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,silence of someone about to
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.31,0:44:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,answer and choosing the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.08,0:44:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't wait for the moment. I
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.85,0:44:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,became a
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.31,0:44:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,person again. I said, my voice
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.10,0:44:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,coming out louder than I wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.01,0:44:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,A game that started before I
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.68,0:44:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,knew I was playing.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.35,0:44:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that what I became? No. Then
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.42,0:44:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,explain. He looked at the table.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.56,0:44:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,He looked at me. He didn't
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.30,0:44:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.41,0:44:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Ludovico. I'll tell you, but not
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.55,0:44:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,now. When. When I'm certain
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.36,0:44:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll hear me out to the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.63,0:44:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I close my eyes for half a
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.96,0:44:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,second. When I opened them, I
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.45,0:44:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,decided that this mansion
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.72,0:44:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,wouldn't hold
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.39,0:44:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,me another hour. I left the
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.06,0:44:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,office without answering. I
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.74,0:44:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,climbed the stairs. Went into my
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.72,0:44:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,room.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.37,0:44:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Put a coat over my dress,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.87,0:44:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,grabbed my purse. I went down
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.61,0:44:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,again. This time without looking
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.53,0:44:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,at any door.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.69,0:44:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I passed on a chair in the
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.22,0:44:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,kitchen. She saw my face and
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.87,0:44:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,didn't ask. I took the key to
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.58,0:44:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,the side door
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.35,0:44:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,no one used and went out through
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.95,0:44:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,the side gravel path. Going
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.31,0:44:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,around the mansion so I wouldn't
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.91,0:45:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,pass by the main entrance. The
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.63,0:45:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,service gate opened onto a
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.13,0:45:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,narrow lane. I followed the lane
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.97,0:45:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,to the street.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.77,0:45:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I followed the street to the bus
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.51,0:45:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,line. I took a bus to the old
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.08,0:45:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,district without looking at
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.55,0:45:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,anyone's face. I needed to walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.56,0:45:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I needed to breathe. I needed to
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.57,0:45:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,remember what it was like to
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.33,0:45:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,have a body that belonged to no
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.98,0:45:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,one. I got off at the stop near
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.64,0:45:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,the old market. The one that
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.13,0:45:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,closes
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.45,0:45:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,after six. Wet stone streets,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.66,0:45:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,yellow lamp posts. Few people at
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.10,0:45:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,that hour, merchants gathering
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.39,0:45:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,crates, a loose dog crossing
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.18,0:45:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,slowly. I shoved my hands into
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.10,0:45:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,my coat pockets and walked with
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.08,0:45:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,no
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.21,0:45:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,destination. The anger pounding
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.00,0:45:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,at the back of my throat. I
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.56,0:45:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,passed the closed bakery,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.63,0:45:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,turned on to a cross street that
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.35,0:45:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,led down to the docks. I walked
Dialogue: 0,0:45:42.01,0:45:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,four blocks. It was at the fifth
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.73,0:45:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,that I noticed. A man in a light
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.49,0:45:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,suit had crossed the street at
Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.14,0:45:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,the same pace as me. On the
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.63,0:45:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,other side,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.73,0:45:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,he wasn't going anywhere. He was
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.69,0:45:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,coming toward me. Renolfo set a
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.58,0:45:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,volley. My step froze for half a
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.54,0:45:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,second
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.91,0:45:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,before I decided to keep walking
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.75,0:45:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,with my chin up. He sped up to
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.48,0:46:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,intercept me at the corner. He
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.21,0:46:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,got too
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.61,0:46:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,close. Mrs. Caratilo. He said
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.02,0:46:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,with the theatrical smile, what
Dialogue: 0,0:46:06.59,0:46:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,luck for me. Excuse
Dialogue: 0,0:46:08.17,0:46:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,me. I tried to pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.31,0:46:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,He stepped to the side, cutting
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.89,0:46:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,off my path without touching me,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.52,0:46:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,but closing off the street.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.43,0:46:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It won't take long. I just
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.07,0:46:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,wanted a minute. I don't have a
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.01,0:46:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,minute. You do. He tilted his
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.84,0:46:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,head
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.09,0:46:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,half a degree. The smile still
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.10,0:46:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,frozen. One thing I need you to
Dialogue: 0,0:46:25.19,0:46:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,know. Okay. Your original debt
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.20,0:46:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,that
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.47,0:46:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,one from the wedding, he made a
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.26,0:46:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,small hand gesture. Like someone
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.11,0:46:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,describing something distant.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:33.33,0:46:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Was with us, Missy. It wasn't
Dialogue: 0,0:46:35.04,0:46:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,with the castanzos. The
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.40,0:46:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,castanzos were just the front.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:38.16,0:46:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You're lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.55,0:46:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not. The smile didn't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.55,0:46:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,And we're still waiting for
Dialogue: 0,0:46:43.29,0:46:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,payment. In person. The air left
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.35,0:46:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,my lungs
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.87,0:46:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,all at once. Get out of my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:47.89,0:46:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a message, Mrs. Caratilo.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:49.85,0:46:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,He leaned half a degree. Still
Dialogue: 0,0:46:51.81,0:46:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,without
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.27,0:46:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,touching me. Tell your husband
Dialogue: 0,0:46:53.78,0:46:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,that we know where he keeps you.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:55.40,0:46:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell him we know where he sent a
Dialogue: 0,0:46:57.57,0:46:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,and tell him that time's running
Dialogue: 0,0:46:59.66,0:47:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,out. Okay. He took a step back.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.68,0:47:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,He gave a nod,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.13,0:47:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,almost courteous. And he was
Dialogue: 0,0:47:04.53,0:47:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,about to exit the scene when a
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.03,0:47:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,car appeared at the top corner
Dialogue: 0,0:47:07.53,0:47:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,with a sharp
Dialogue: 0,0:47:08.13,0:47:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,breaking. The headlight hitting
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.93,0:47:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,him straight in the face.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.39,0:47:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Renolfo raised his hand to
Dialogue: 0,0:47:12.90,0:47:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,shield his eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:14.39,0:47:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Bastion leapt from the driver's
Dialogue: 0,0:47:15.81,0:47:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,seat with his hand inside his
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.13,0:47:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,coat at the level of the
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.22,0:47:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,holster.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:19.11,0:47:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Get in, ma'am. That was all he
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.97,0:47:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,said. Renolfo raised both hands
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.90,0:47:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,with theatrical calm. Like
Dialogue: 0,0:47:24.52,0:47:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,someone
Dialogue: 0,0:47:24.95,0:47:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,who wasn't doing anything wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.60,0:47:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,He stepped back two paces into
Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.14,0:47:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,the shadow of the corner. He
Dialogue: 0,0:47:29.58,0:47:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,disappeared
Dialogue: 0,0:47:30.15,0:47:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,into an alley before Bastion
Dialogue: 0,0:47:31.57,0:47:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,could take another step. I got
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.10,0:47:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,into the car with legs that were
Dialogue: 0,0:47:34.73,0:47:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,no
Dialogue: 0,0:47:34.83,0:47:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,longer entirely mine. Bastion
Dialogue: 0,0:47:36.66,0:47:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,slammed the door. He turned the
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.61,0:47:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,car onto the cross street. The
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.50,0:47:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,accelerated
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.19,0:47:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,enough to leave the old district
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.93,0:47:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,in less than three minutes,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:44.39,0:47:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,without speaking to me. Only
Dialogue: 0,0:47:45.91,0:47:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,when we got
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.51,0:47:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,onto the road climbing to the
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.78,0:47:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,upper neighborhood did he look
Dialogue: 0,0:47:49.09,0:47:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,at the rear view mirror. Are you
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.49,0:47:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,all right,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.93,0:47:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine. You don't look at. I
Dialogue: 0,0:47:53.61,0:47:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,ran my hand over my face.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:55.84,0:47:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Bastion, ma 'am. How
Dialogue: 0,0:47:57.63,0:47:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,did you find me? He didn't
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.19,0:48:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,answer for half a block. Mr.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.04,0:48:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Ludovico asked someone to never
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.10,0:48:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,lose sight of you. Never. Since
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.15,0:48:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,the
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.35,0:48:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,day of the cafe, you follow me?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.52,0:48:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We look out for you. It's not
Dialogue: 0,0:48:09.54,0:48:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,the same thing. It's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:11.29,0:48:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Bastion looked
Dialogue: 0,0:48:12.27,0:48:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,ahead. But in this case it
Dialogue: 0,0:48:13.98,0:48:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,worked out to be similar. I
Dialogue: 0,0:48:15.76,0:48:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,stayed quiet the rest of the
Dialogue: 0,0:48:17.60,0:48:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,way. My face
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.39,0:48:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,turned to the window and a
Dialogue: 0,0:48:19.73,0:48:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,mixture of things in my throat
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.28,0:48:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,that I couldn't separate. Anger
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.88,0:48:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,at having
Dialogue: 0,0:48:23.35,0:48:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,been followed. Relief at having
Dialogue: 0,0:48:25.68,0:48:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,been followed. Shame at both.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:27.86,0:48:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Renolfo had said two sentences
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.11,0:48:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,that were
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.79,0:48:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,already burying themselves in
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.44,0:48:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,the exact spot where they'd hurt
Dialogue: 0,0:48:34.26,0:48:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,later. Your original debt was
Dialogue: 0,0:48:35.91,0:48:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.73,0:48:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell your husband that we know
Dialogue: 0,0:48:38.17,0:48:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,where he keeps you. Bastion said
Dialogue: 0,0:48:39.71,0:48:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,one last sentence before we
Dialogue: 0,0:48:41.00,0:48:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,parked
Dialogue: 0,0:48:41.29,0:48:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,on the gravel. Mr. Ludovico will
Dialogue: 0,0:48:43.37,0:48:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,want to talk. Better to let him
Dialogue: 0,0:48:45.38,0:48:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,speak to the end this time. I
Dialogue: 0,0:48:47.26,0:48:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,didn't
Dialogue: 0,0:48:47.65,0:48:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,answer. I got out of the car. I
Dialogue: 0,0:48:49.50,0:48:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,climbed the three steps of the
Dialogue: 0,0:48:51.28,0:48:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,entrance. The main door was
Dialogue: 0,0:48:52.89,0:48:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,already
Dialogue: 0,0:48:53.31,0:48:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,open. Ludovico was at the foot
Dialogue: 0,0:48:55.48,0:48:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,of the stairs. No jacket. No
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.51,0:48:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,tie. His sleeves still rolled up
Dialogue: 0,0:48:59.82,0:49:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,at the elbow
Dialogue: 0,0:49:00.69,0:49:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,the way they were in the
Dialogue: 0,0:49:02.28,0:49:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,library. He wasn't angry. He was
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.39,0:49:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,something worse. He was afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:06.44,0:49:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,And Ludovico
Dialogue: 0,0:49:07.23,0:49:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Karachiollo afraid was something
Dialogue: 0,0:49:09.44,0:49:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,all of Providence had never
Dialogue: 0,0:49:11.31,0:49:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,seen. And I, without meaning to
Dialogue: 0,0:49:13.45,0:49:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,saw,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:13.73,0:49:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,he had a folder in his hand. It
Dialogue: 0,0:49:15.56,0:49:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,wasn't the folder from the back
Dialogue: 0,0:49:17.40,0:49:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,office. It was another folder.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:19.73,0:49:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Thicker. Heldunder his arm with
Dialogue: 0,0:49:21.32,0:49:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,a car that didn't match the rest
Dialogue: 0,0:49:22.97,0:49:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,of his body. He lowered his chin
Dialogue: 0,0:49:24.61,0:49:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,half a degree. He looked at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:26.58,0:49:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And for the first time since the
Dialogue: 0,0:49:28.61,0:49:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,cafe, his voice came out without
Dialogue: 0,0:49:30.64,0:49:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,any
Dialogue: 0,0:49:30.83,0:49:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,mask. Say, I'm
Dialogue: 0,0:49:37.68,0:49:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,going to tell you everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:39.31,0:49:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The folder under his arm was too
Dialogue: 0,0:49:41.11,0:49:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,thick. I recognized
Dialogue: 0,0:49:42.18,0:49:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,the worn leather from far off.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:43.91,0:49:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The same color as the one I'd
Dialogue: 0,0:49:45.58,0:49:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,seen in the back room. Tuesday
Dialogue: 0,0:49:47.30,0:49:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,afternoon,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:47.88,0:49:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,with the photo of a delmo and
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.87,0:49:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Newark inside. Ludovico was at
Dialogue: 0,0:49:51.93,0:49:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,the foot of the stairs. As
Dialogue: 0,0:49:53.72,0:49:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Bastion had worn in the car. And
Dialogue: 0,0:49:55.81,0:49:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,there was no mask at all on his
Dialogue: 0,0:49:57.84,0:49:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,face. Only weariness. And
Dialogue: 0,0:49:59.47,0:50:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,something
Dialogue: 0,0:50:00.06,0:50:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,deeper that I couldn't name. And
Dialogue: 0,0:50:02.05,0:50:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,that squeezed my chest before I
Dialogue: 0,0:50:03.99,0:50:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,could defend myself. Sit. He
Dialogue: 0,0:50:05.73,0:50:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,said
Dialogue: 0,0:50:05.98,0:50:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,low. When I came in through the
Dialogue: 0,0:50:07.92,0:50:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,door. I didn't obey at first. I
Dialogue: 0,0:50:09.86,0:50:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,stood there with my coat wet
Dialogue: 0,0:50:11.61,0:50:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,from
Dialogue: 0,0:50:11.86,0:50:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,the old district's drizzle stuck
Dialogue: 0,0:50:14.02,0:50:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,to my shoulders. Still tasting
Dialogue: 0,0:50:16.04,0:50:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,the metallic taste that the
Dialogue: 0,0:50:17.86,0:50:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,mouth, Bastion came in behind
Dialogue: 0,0:50:19.71,0:50:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,me. Looked at his boss. Looked
Dialogue: 0,0:50:21.63,0:50:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,at me. And disappeared down the
Dialogue: 0,0:50:23.61,0:50:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,kitchen
Dialogue: 0,0:50:24.06,0:50:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,corridor without a word. Don't
Dialogue: 0,0:50:25.62,0:50:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,let you out of didn't appear.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:27.12,0:50:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The mansion seemed to have
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.47,0:50:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,agreed
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.78,0:50:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,with her to hold its breath.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:30.79,0:50:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Sit, Elanda. Please. The please
Dialogue: 0,0:50:33.01,0:50:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,was what moved me. I'd never
Dialogue: 0,0:50:35.02,0:50:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,heard
Dialogue: 0,0:50:35.38,0:50:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,that word from his mouth. I sat
Dialogue: 0,0:50:37.10,0:50:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,in one of the library arm chairs
Dialogue: 0,0:50:38.87,0:50:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,where he guided me. And he
Dialogue: 0,0:50:40.31,0:50:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,pulled
Dialogue: 0,0:50:40.64,0:50:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,the other one and turned it to
Dialogue: 0,0:50:42.33,0:50:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,face me. So close our knees
Dialogue: 0,0:50:43.85,0:50:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,almost touched. He said the
Dialogue: 0,0:50:45.37,0:50:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,folder on
Dialogue: 0,0:50:45.88,0:50:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,little table between us. He
Dialogue: 0,0:50:47.56,0:50:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,didn't open it. What I'm about
Dialogue: 0,0:50:49.43,0:50:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,to tell you, you've had the
Dialogue: 0,0:50:51.11,0:50:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,right to know
Dialogue: 0,0:50:51.92,0:50:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,for weeks. He began. His voice
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.97,0:50:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,horser than it usually was. I
Dialogue: 0,0:50:55.96,0:50:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,put it off because I was afraid
Dialogue: 0,0:50:58.08,0:50:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,you'd
Dialogue: 0,0:50:58.42,0:51:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,get up and leave before the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:00.59,0:51:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Today if you get up, you get up.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:02.77,0:51:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't hold you. My jaw locked.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:05.50,0:51:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I made a small gesture with my
Dialogue: 0,0:51:07.06,0:51:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,head for him to go on. Ludovico
Dialogue: 0,0:51:08.66,0:51:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,opened the folder and took out
Dialogue: 0,0:51:10.22,0:51:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,three
Dialogue: 0,0:51:10.48,0:51:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,sheets. He didn't look at them.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:12.56,0:51:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Adelmo owed the cerevaules. He
Dialogue: 0,0:51:14.58,0:51:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,said, he'd owed them for over a
Dialogue: 0,0:51:16.66,0:51:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,year.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:17.40,0:51:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't gambling. It wasn't an
Dialogue: 0,0:51:19.18,0:51:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,end of the month vice. He got
Dialogue: 0,0:51:20.78,0:51:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,into a deal with Renolfo
Dialogue: 0,0:51:22.12,0:51:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,thinking
Dialogue: 0,0:51:22.56,0:51:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,he'd come out rich and came out
Dialogue: 0,0:51:24.41,0:51:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,owing $35,000. And a promise he
Dialogue: 0,0:51:26.25,0:51:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,didn't have the courage to tell
Dialogue: 0,0:51:28.10,0:51:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,you
Dialogue: 0,0:51:28.28,0:51:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,about. Adelmo's name and his
Dialogue: 0,0:51:29.92,0:51:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,mouth sounded distant. As if he
Dialogue: 0,0:51:31.73,0:51:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,were speaking of a man I'd known
Dialogue: 0,0:51:33.60,0:51:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,in
Dialogue: 0,0:51:33.72,0:51:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,another life. Maybe he was. The
Dialogue: 0,0:51:36.09,0:51:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,promise was you. He continued.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:38.38,0:51:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,His eyes fixed on mine. The
Dialogue: 0,0:51:40.44,0:51:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,deal between Adelmo and the
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.87,0:51:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Calabrian clan was simple. On
Dialogue: 0,0:51:43.42,0:51:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,the wedding day, the cerevaules
Dialogue: 0,0:51:45.06,0:51:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,would appear
Dialogue: 0,0:51:45.70,0:51:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,at the church. Adelmo would sign
Dialogue: 0,0:51:47.47,0:51:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,whatever he needed to sign and
Dialogue: 0,0:51:49.13,0:51:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,disappear through the back door.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:51.40,0:51:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd leave with them. His debt
Dialogue: 0,0:51:53.21,0:51:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,would be forgiven. You'd be the
Dialogue: 0,0:51:55.03,0:51:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,payment in person.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:56.60,0:51:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Something inside me went cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:58.63,0:52:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,In a way that left no tremor.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:00.59,0:52:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Only silence. I clashed my hands
Dialogue: 0,0:52:02.76,0:52:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,in my
Dialogue: 0,0:52:03.10,0:52:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,lap so I wouldn't move. The
Dialogue: 0,0:52:04.98,0:52:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,wedding debt. He said, was built
Dialogue: 0,0:52:07.20,0:52:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,on top of that. The castanzo
Dialogue: 0,0:52:09.14,0:52:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,brothers
Dialogue: 0,0:52:09.70,0:52:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,have been a front for the
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.02,0:52:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,cerevaules for three years. They
Dialogue: 0,0:52:12.71,0:52:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,collected your signature in the
Dialogue: 0,0:52:14.34,0:52:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,middle
Dialogue: 0,0:52:14.66,0:52:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,of the venue papers because they
Dialogue: 0,0:52:16.08,0:52:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,needed a rope around your neck
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.42,0:52:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,in case the church plan failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:19.32,0:52:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Two traps for the same day. One
Dialogue: 0,0:52:21.13,0:52:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,for you to walk in wearing
Dialogue: 0,0:52:22.66,0:52:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,white. Another so you'd have
Dialogue: 0,0:52:24.29,0:52:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,nowhere to
Dialogue: 0,0:52:24.88,0:52:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,run if the white dress wasn't
Dialogue: 0,0:52:26.63,0:52:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,enough. How did you find out? I
Dialogue: 0,0:52:28.51,0:52:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,said, and my voice came out
Dialogue: 0,0:52:30.14,0:52:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,steady,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:31.12,0:52:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,which surprised me. Three days
Dialogue: 0,0:52:32.88,0:52:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,before the wedding. My lawyer
Dialogue: 0,0:52:34.57,0:52:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,has an old informant in
Dialogue: 0,0:52:35.92,0:52:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,the
Dialogue: 0,0:52:39.68,0:52:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,house. The name crossed his desk
Dialogue: 0,0:52:41.57,0:52:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,by accident. Linked to Renolfo,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:43.41,0:52:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Linked to yours. He brought it
Dialogue: 0,0:52:45.18,0:52:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,to
Dialogue: 0,0:52:45.30,0:52:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,me that same night. He stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:47.34,0:52:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Ranna's hand over his face. Then
Dialogue: 0,0:52:49.45,0:52:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,continued. I went after Adelmo
Dialogue: 0,0:52:51.42,0:52:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,that same early morning. I
Dialogue: 0,0:52:52.94,0:52:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,caught him at his place with a
Dialogue: 0,0:52:54.70,0:52:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,bag packed for another city that
Dialogue: 0,0:52:56.57,0:52:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,wasn't
Dialogue: 0,0:52:56.92,0:52:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,the one he told you. He
Dialogue: 0,0:52:58.33,0:52:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,confessed everything in 20
Dialogue: 0,0:52:59.92,0:53:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,minutes. He cried. He begged
Dialogue: 0,0:53:01.64,0:53:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,forgiveness from the
Dialogue: 0,0:53:02.86,0:53:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,wall, not from you. I gave him
Dialogue: 0,0:53:04.78,0:53:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,two options. He disappears from
Dialogue: 0,0:53:06.77,0:53:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Providence before dawn,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:08.24,0:53:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,with enough money to reach
Dialogue: 0,0:53:09.67,0:53:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Newark and live quietly. Or I
Dialogue: 0,0:53:11.26,0:53:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,let the Sarah Falls find out he
Dialogue: 0,0:53:12.96,0:53:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,tried to escape
Dialogue: 0,0:53:13.78,0:53:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,the deal. He chose Newark before
Dialogue: 0,0:53:15.76,0:53:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I finished the sentence. I
Dialogue: 0,0:53:17.37,0:53:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,closed my eyes. I saw Adelmo at
Dialogue: 0,0:53:19.28,0:53:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,the church
Dialogue: 0,0:53:19.90,0:53:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,in his suit, smiling for photos
Dialogue: 0,0:53:21.92,0:53:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,the week before. I saw the
Dialogue: 0,0:53:23.62,0:53:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,church bell tolling 12 times. I
Dialogue: 0,0:53:25.64,0:53:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,opened them
Dialogue: 0,0:53:26.36,0:53:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,again. You made him abandoned me
Dialogue: 0,0:53:28.30,0:53:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,at the altar. I made him abandon
Dialogue: 0,0:53:30.24,0:53:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,you before he sold you. The
Dialogue: 0,0:53:31.88,0:53:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,distinction landed between us
Dialogue: 0,0:53:33.31,0:53:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,like an open blade. It didn't
Dialogue: 0,0:53:34.74,0:53:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,hurt me the way it should have
Dialogue: 0,0:53:36.21,0:53:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:36.46,0:53:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It just stayed there gleaming.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:38.84,0:53:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The bell, I said. And the bell
Dialogue: 0,0:53:41.22,0:53:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,returned inside my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:43.60,0:53:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Tolling slowly. You let the bell
Dialogue: 0,0:53:45.46,0:53:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,toll. I couldn't stop the bell
Dialogue: 0,0:53:47.21,0:53:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,without stopping the town.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:49.14,0:53:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,If I'd shown up at the church
Dialogue: 0,0:53:50.58,0:53:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,pulling you away by the arm, the
Dialogue: 0,0:53:52.16,0:53:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Sarah Falls would know within
Dialogue: 0,0:53:53.60,0:53:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,two hours that I'd stepped in.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:55.52,0:53:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd become a double target and
Dialogue: 0,0:53:57.57,0:53:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd become a war. I let the bell
Dialogue: 0,0:53:59.62,0:54:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,toll because humiliation passes.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:01.74,0:54:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The bullet doesn't. I swallowed
Dialogue: 0,0:54:03.80,0:54:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,hard. My mouth was dry in a
Dialogue: 0,0:54:05.60,0:54:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,strange
Dialogue: 0,0:54:06.06,0:54:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,way. The next day, he said, I
Dialogue: 0,0:54:08.37,0:54:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,bought the Costanzo's debt. I
Dialogue: 0,0:54:10.69,0:54:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,paid the $12,000 in your name
Dialogue: 0,0:54:13.00,0:54:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,plus the rest the Sarah Falls
Dialogue: 0,0:54:14.85,0:54:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,expected to receive on the side.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:16.89,0:54:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Two hours later, I had the paper
Dialogue: 0,0:54:18.94,0:54:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,in my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:20.46,0:54:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You no longer owed anyone
Dialogue: 0,0:54:21.77,0:54:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,anything. Except you didn't know
Dialogue: 0,0:54:23.44,0:54:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,that. And I couldn't come
Dialogue: 0,0:54:24.75,0:54:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,looking for
Dialogue: 0,0:54:25.32,0:54:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,you without the Sarah Falls
Dialogue: 0,0:54:26.60,0:54:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,understanding that their
Dialogue: 0,0:54:27.74,0:54:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,merchandise had a new owner. So
Dialogue: 0,0:54:29.21,0:54:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,you waited
Dialogue: 0,0:54:29.68,0:54:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,for me to lose my job. My
Dialogue: 0,0:54:31.35,0:54:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,apartment, my name. I waited for
Dialogue: 0,0:54:33.50,0:54:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,you to lose everything that
Dialogue: 0,0:54:35.31,0:54:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,still
Dialogue: 0,0:54:35.64,0:54:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,tied you to the town. He said,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:37.47,0:54:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,and his voice finally wavered
Dialogue: 0,0:54:39.24,0:54:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,because if I'd knocked on your
Dialogue: 0,0:54:41.08,0:54:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,door
Dialogue: 0,0:54:41.32,0:54:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,with money on Monday, you'd
Dialogue: 0,0:54:42.91,0:54:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,throw it in my face. If I'd
Dialogue: 0,0:54:44.50,0:54:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,knocked on your door on
Dialogue: 0,0:54:45.85,0:54:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Wednesday,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:47.08,0:54:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,with you already having nowhere
Dialogue: 0,0:54:49.04,0:54:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,to go, you'd listen to me. I
Dialogue: 0,0:54:50.82,0:54:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,played you. I won't pretend I
Dialogue: 0,0:54:52.66,0:54:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:53.56,0:54:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The silence pressed down. I
Dialogue: 0,0:54:55.43,0:54:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,heard my own pulse in my ear.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:57.43,0:54:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The contract. I said,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:59.16,0:55:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,it was the only way I saw to
Dialogue: 0,0:55:00.56,0:55:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,have you under this roof without
Dialogue: 0,0:55:02.15,0:55:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,the Sarah Falls understanding
Dialogue: 0,0:55:03.60,0:55:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,what
Dialogue: 0,0:55:03.80,0:55:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,was. If you became my wife on
Dialogue: 0,0:55:05.69,0:55:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,paper, you became untouchable in
Dialogue: 0,0:55:07.78,0:55:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Providence. No one touches the
Dialogue: 0,0:55:09.73,0:55:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Don's
Dialogue: 0,0:55:10.06,0:55:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,wife without starting a war. No
Dialogue: 0,0:55:12.05,0:55:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,one wants to start. The whole
Dialogue: 0,0:55:13.90,0:55:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,coldness, the separate rooms,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:16.12,0:55:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,the rules, the no questions, was
Dialogue: 0,0:55:18.34,0:55:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,to give you space, not to
Dialogue: 0,0:55:20.08,0:55:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,control you. I didn't know how
Dialogue: 0,0:55:22.16,0:55:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,to offer
Dialogue: 0,0:55:22.72,0:55:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,you protection without it
Dialogue: 0,0:55:24.29,0:55:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,looking like a prison. I chose
Dialogue: 0,0:55:26.17,0:55:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,wrong. I chose too cold. I
Dialogue: 0,0:55:27.80,0:55:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,stayed quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:28.62,0:55:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,He waited. He didn't try to fill
Dialogue: 0,0:55:30.88,0:55:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,it. And a Delmo? I said
Dialogue: 0,0:55:32.51,0:55:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,afterward. The photo in Newark.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:35.26,0:55:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I pay a man to keep an eye on
Dialogue: 0,0:55:36.74,0:55:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,him. Not because I care about a
Dialogue: 0,0:55:38.33,0:55:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Delmo. Because as long as he's
Dialogue: 0,0:55:39.86,0:55:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,alive
Dialogue: 0,0:55:40.12,0:55:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,in some corner, the Sarah Falls
Dialogue: 0,0:55:41.79,0:55:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,think the original deal can
Dialogue: 0,0:55:43.25,0:55:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,still be collected. The day he
Dialogue: 0,0:55:44.86,0:55:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,decides
Dialogue: 0,0:55:45.24,0:55:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,to come back to Providence
Dialogue: 0,0:55:46.65,0:55:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,thinking he can turn the tables.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:48.39,0:55:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to know before he does.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:50.02,0:55:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what
Dialogue: 0,0:55:50.62,0:55:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,that note meant. Silence paid.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:52.86,0:55:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,His silence. Not mine with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:55.17,0:55:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I stood up. I didn't know where
Dialogue: 0,0:55:57.49,0:55:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I was
Dialogue: 0,0:55:58.34,0:55:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I only knew I couldn't stay
Dialogue: 0,0:55:59.90,0:56:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,sitting. I walked to the library
Dialogue: 0,0:56:01.74,0:56:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,window, leaned my forehead
Dialogue: 0,0:56:03.24,0:56:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,against
Dialogue: 0,0:56:03.64,0:56:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,the glass, and looked at the
Dialogue: 0,0:56:05.27,0:56:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,dark garden. His reflection
Dialogue: 0,0:56:06.84,0:56:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,appeared behind mine in the
Dialogue: 0,0:56:08.41,0:56:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,glass.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:09.32,0:56:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Seated. Still waiting. I need
Dialogue: 0,0:56:11.78,0:56:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,air. I said, go. I left the
Dialogue: 0,0:56:14.08,0:56:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,library with a firm step and
Dialogue: 0,0:56:16.46,0:56:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,went down
Dialogue: 0,0:56:17.22,0:56:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,the corridor to the back of
Dialogue: 0,0:56:18.68,0:56:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Miranda. The drizzle had
Dialogue: 0,0:56:19.98,0:56:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,stopped. The winter garden had
Dialogue: 0,0:56:21.60,0:56:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,its light low,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:22.74,0:56:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,and the veranda was empty. I
Dialogue: 0,0:56:24.18,0:56:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,leaned against the iron railing
Dialogue: 0,0:56:25.78,0:56:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,and breath deeply for the first
Dialogue: 0,0:56:27.37,0:56:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,time
Dialogue: 0,0:56:27.58,0:56:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,in an hour. And then I cried. I
Dialogue: 0,0:56:29.60,0:56:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,didn't cry over a Delmo. I cried
Dialogue: 0,0:56:31.69,0:56:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,over the weeks I'd slept in that
Dialogue: 0,0:56:33.78,0:56:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,room thinking I was merchandise.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:35.64,0:56:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I cried over the church bell,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:37.32,0:56:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,tolding 12 times. Knowing now
Dialogue: 0,0:56:39.01,0:56:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,that
Dialogue: 0,0:56:39.24,0:56:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,behind that bell, there had been
Dialogue: 0,0:56:40.95,0:56:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,a plan to hand me over behind a
Dialogue: 0,0:56:42.60,0:56:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,cabinet. I cried over the glass
Dialogue: 0,0:56:44.26,0:56:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,of water he'd set beside my knee
Dialogue: 0,0:56:46.11,0:56:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,in the kitchen weeks ago, and
Dialogue: 0,0:56:47.78,0:56:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,that I'd seen at the time as
Dialogue: 0,0:56:49.40,0:56:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,elegant coldness. And now saw as
Dialogue: 0,0:56:51.50,0:56:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,the only thing he knew how to do
Dialogue: 0,0:56:53.61,0:56:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,without frightening me.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:55.92,0:56:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I cried because I'd spent weeks
Dialogue: 0,0:56:57.49,0:56:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,thinking I was his shield when
Dialogue: 0,0:56:59.00,0:57:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,in fact he was the one who had
Dialogue: 0,0:57:00.52,0:57:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,become mine. He didn't come
Dialogue: 0,0:57:02.41,0:57:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,after me. I stayed there until
Dialogue: 0,0:57:04.52,0:57:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,the sky went fully dark. When I
Dialogue: 0,0:57:06.69,0:57:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,went back
Dialogue: 0,0:57:07.32,0:57:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,to the library, he was still
Dialogue: 0,0:57:08.85,0:57:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,sitting in the same armchair.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:10.42,0:57:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The folder closed on the little
Dialogue: 0,0:57:12.11,0:57:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,table.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:12.90,0:57:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,His hands and his lap
Dialogue: 0,0:57:14.24,0:57:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,intertwined. You should have
Dialogue: 0,0:57:16.02,0:57:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,told me. I said from the
Dialogue: 0,0:57:17.55,0:57:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,doorway. I was going to tell
Dialogue: 0,0:57:19.34,0:57:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,you when you no longer needed
Dialogue: 0,0:57:21.20,0:57:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,me. He said, without raising his
Dialogue: 0,0:57:23.24,0:57:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,eyes, that sentence landed in
Dialogue: 0,0:57:25.10,0:57:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,strange way. I stood there
Dialogue: 0,0:57:27.04,0:57:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,absorbing it. That's pride,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:29.06,0:57:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Lutavico. I said, low. That's
Dialogue: 0,0:57:31.22,0:57:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,fear with a
Dialogue: 0,0:57:32.04,0:57:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,pretty name. He raised his eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:34.97,0:57:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't look away. It is. He
Dialogue: 0,0:57:37.72,0:57:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,said, I know. I
Dialogue: 0,0:57:39.10,0:57:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,sat back down in the armchair
Dialogue: 0,0:57:40.44,0:57:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,across from him. I looked at him
Dialogue: 0,0:57:42.22,0:57:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,for a stretch of time. I didn't
Dialogue: 0,0:57:43.95,0:57:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,measure. He didn't rush me.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:45.46,0:57:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:46.68,0:57:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I said, finally, I want the
Dialogue: 0,0:57:48.58,0:57:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,three elders here. In this hall,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:50.84,0:57:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to speak with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:52.88,0:57:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'llanda, I'm calling them. Not
Dialogue: 0,0:57:54.97,0:57:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,you. They called me a bot bride
Dialogue: 0,0:57:57.05,0:57:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,behind my back. I want them to
Dialogue: 0,0:57:59.07,0:57:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,hear
Dialogue: 0,0:57:59.34,0:58:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,me face to face. He was silent
Dialogue: 0,0:58:01.37,0:58:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,for a few seconds. Then he said,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:03.53,0:58:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,tomorrow night. Tomorrow night,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:05.96,0:58:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I stood up and went up the
Dialogue: 0,0:58:07.32,0:58:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,stairs slowly. I didn't go to my
Dialogue: 0,0:58:08.98,0:58:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,room. I walked to the end of the
Dialogue: 0,0:58:10.65,0:58:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,left
Dialogue: 0,0:58:10.86,0:58:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,corridor. Stopped at the door
Dialogue: 0,0:58:12.56,0:58:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd never opened and went back
Dialogue: 0,0:58:14.31,0:58:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,to my room because it wasn't yet
Dialogue: 0,0:58:16.19,0:58:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,time.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:16.82,0:58:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,But I knew it was a matter of
Dialogue: 0,0:58:18.57,0:58:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,hours. I slept little. I dreamed
Dialogue: 0,0:58:20.50,0:58:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,of the church bell
Dialogue: 0,0:58:21.58,0:58:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,holding 12 times and of his hand
Dialogue: 0,0:58:23.69,0:58:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,setting a glass of water beside
Dialogue: 0,0:58:25.74,0:58:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,my knee. The next night,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:27.70,0:58:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,the main hall was lit as if for
Dialogue: 0,0:58:29.61,0:58:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,a family dinner. And it wasn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:31.52,0:58:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The three elders arrived 15
Dialogue: 0,0:58:33.19,0:58:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,minutes
Dialogue: 0,0:58:33.62,0:58:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,apart from each other. Don
Dialogue: 0,0:58:35.17,0:58:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Vittario came first. Tall and
Dialogue: 0,0:58:36.89,0:58:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,thin with a silk scarf inside
Dialogue: 0,0:58:38.62,0:58:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,his
Dialogue: 0,0:58:38.80,0:58:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,overcoat. Don Emiliano next.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:40.86,0:58:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Stokki with the crest of the
Dialogue: 0,0:58:42.92,0:58:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,split crown lion on his pinky
Dialogue: 0,0:58:45.05,0:58:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,ring
Dialogue: 0,0:58:45.34,0:58:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,and an unlit cigarette between
Dialogue: 0,0:58:47.47,0:58:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,his fingers. Don Cisto last bent
Dialogue: 0,0:58:49.75,0:58:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,by the ears with a silver
Dialogue: 0,0:58:51.52,0:58:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,handled
Dialogue: 0,0:58:52.02,0:58:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,cane. The family lawyer, Fausto
Dialogue: 0,0:58:54.09,0:58:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Renieri, the same one Lutavico
Dialogue: 0,0:58:56.09,0:58:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,had mentioned in the library,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:58.76,0:59:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,arrived alongside the hardest of
Dialogue: 0,0:59:00.32,0:59:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,the three and stood leaning
Dialogue: 0,0:59:01.64,0:59:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,against one of the columns,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:03.52,0:59:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,silent, bastion stayed at the
Dialogue: 0,0:59:05.19,0:59:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,door. Lutavico waited on the
Dialogue: 0,0:59:06.81,0:59:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,other side of the hall,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:08.44,0:59:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,without interfering. I came down
Dialogue: 0,0:59:10.20,0:59:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,the stairs and the dark blue
Dialogue: 0,0:59:11.75,0:59:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,dress Donutiara had laid on the
Dialogue: 0,0:59:13.45,0:59:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,bed
Dialogue: 0,0:59:13.62,0:59:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,for me without asking. I stopped
Dialogue: 0,0:59:15.32,0:59:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,in the middle of the hall. The
Dialogue: 0,0:59:16.92,0:59:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,three elders looked at me the
Dialogue: 0,0:59:18.46,0:59:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,way
Dialogue: 0,0:59:18.62,0:59:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,you look at an expensive piece
Dialogue: 0,0:59:20.60,0:59:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,of China, assessing whether it's
Dialogue: 0,0:59:22.72,0:59:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,cracked. Gentlemen, I said,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:25.00,0:59:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,and my voice came out steady.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:26.64,0:59:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The three of you, at some point
Dialogue: 0,0:59:28.40,0:59:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,in the last month, called me a
Dialogue: 0,0:59:30.10,0:59:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,bride bought in some corner of
Dialogue: 0,0:59:31.71,0:59:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,this house. I know this because
Dialogue: 0,0:59:33.37,0:59:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,this house is large but not
Dialogue: 0,0:59:34.82,0:59:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,large enough
Dialogue: 0,0:59:35.46,0:59:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,for a whisper not to climb the
Dialogue: 0,0:59:37.69,0:59:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,stairs. Girl, Don Cisto began,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:39.91,0:59:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,his voice rasping. This is not
Dialogue: 0,0:59:42.14,0:59:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,the
Dialogue: 0,0:59:42.36,0:59:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,place for, I raised my hand. Let
Dialogue: 0,0:59:44.66,0:59:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,me finish. I was bought, yes,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:46.74,0:59:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,you're right about that part,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:49.20,0:59:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,but you're getting wrong as
Dialogue: 0,0:59:50.75,0:59:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,about the merchandise. The
Dialogue: 0,0:59:52.24,0:59:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,merchandise wasn't me. It was my
Dialogue: 0,0:59:54.07,0:59:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,life,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:54.64,0:59:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,and whoever paid for it paid so
Dialogue: 0,0:59:56.14,0:59:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,that it wouldn't be taken from
Dialogue: 0,0:59:57.60,0:59:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,me by another clan. You know
Dialogue: 0,0:59:58.96,0:59:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,which
Dialogue: 0,0:59:59.20,1:00:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,clan. You know by whom. I saw
Dialogue: 0,1:00:01.07,1:00:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Donut, Miliano exchange a look
Dialogue: 0,1:00:03.01,1:00:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,with Donvittorio. I continued.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:05.54,1:00:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't come here to ask you to
Dialogue: 0,1:00:07.42,1:00:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,like me. It's none of my
Dialogue: 0,1:00:08.83,1:00:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,concern. I came to say only one
Dialogue: 0,1:00:10.65,1:00:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:11.00,1:00:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I chose to stay. Not because of
Dialogue: 0,1:00:13.00,1:00:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,the contract. The contract still
Dialogue: 0,1:00:15.06,1:00:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,has almost a year to go,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:16.86,1:00:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,and you know better than anyone
Dialogue: 0,1:00:18.82,1:00:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,that paper tears. I stay because
Dialogue: 0,1:00:20.85,1:00:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I chose to. No clause, no exit
Dialogue: 0,1:00:22.74,1:00:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,door,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:23.26,1:00:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,no price. My gaze crossed
Dialogue: 0,1:00:24.68,1:00:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Ludovico's from the other side
Dialogue: 0,1:00:26.39,1:00:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,of the hall. He understood I was
Dialogue: 0,1:00:28.21,1:00:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,speaking to
Dialogue: 0,1:00:28.84,1:00:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,him too. His hand closed slowly
Dialogue: 0,1:00:30.55,1:00:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,around his own wrist. In the
Dialogue: 0,1:00:32.09,1:00:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,place where he wore his father's
Dialogue: 0,1:00:33.85,1:00:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,watch.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:34.68,1:00:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all. I said to the
Dialogue: 0,1:00:36.34,1:00:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,elders, good night. I turned and
Dialogue: 0,1:00:38.46,1:00:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,went up the stairs. I didn't
Dialogue: 0,1:00:40.31,1:00:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,look
Dialogue: 0,1:00:40.58,1:00:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,back to know whether he was
Dialogue: 0,1:00:41.98,1:00:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,coming. I knew he was. He caught
Dialogue: 0,1:00:43.64,1:00:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,up with me in the middle of the
Dialogue: 0,1:00:45.24,1:00:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,upper
Dialogue: 0,1:00:45.50,1:00:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,corridor. He didn't speak. I
Dialogue: 0,1:00:46.98,1:00:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,walked three more steps and
Dialogue: 0,1:00:48.40,1:00:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,stopped in front of the door at
Dialogue: 0,1:00:50.03,1:00:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,the end of
Dialogue: 0,1:00:50.56,1:00:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,the left corridor. His mind was
Dialogue: 0,1:00:52.77,1:00:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,three doors back on the right.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:54.91,1:00:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,He stopped behind me. So close I
Dialogue: 0,1:00:57.19,1:00:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,felt his
Dialogue: 0,1:00:57.76,1:00:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,breath in my hair. I turned
Dialogue: 0,1:00:59.49,1:01:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,slowly. His eyes were dark in a
Dialogue: 0,1:01:01.48,1:01:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,new way, and his hand rose until
Dialogue: 0,1:01:03.54,1:01:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,it almost touched my face and
Dialogue: 0,1:01:05.19,1:01:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,stopped in the air, waiting. I
Dialogue: 0,1:01:06.89,1:01:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,took his hand and pressed it to
Dialogue: 0,1:01:08.65,1:01:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,my
Dialogue: 0,1:01:08.76,1:01:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,face myself. He let out his
Dialogue: 0,1:01:10.15,1:01:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,breath like someone who'd been
Dialogue: 0,1:01:11.69,1:01:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,holding it for months.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:18.33,1:01:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,His hand was warm
Dialogue: 0,1:01:19.13,1:01:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,on my cheek. Mine over his,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:21.20,1:01:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,trembled for half a second and
Dialogue: 0,1:01:23.50,1:01:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,stopped. If you come in here, he
Dialogue: 0,1:01:25.95,1:01:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,said,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:26.53,1:01:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,low, his eyes on mine. There's
Dialogue: 0,1:01:28.61,1:01:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,no more contract between us.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:30.56,1:01:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Good. I said, he leaned his
Dialogue: 0,1:01:32.43,1:01:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,forehead
Dialogue: 0,1:01:32.99,1:01:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,against mine. We stayed there,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:34.90,1:01:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,breathing the same air of the
Dialogue: 0,1:01:36.74,1:01:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,corridor. The sounds
Dialogue: 0,1:01:38.01,1:01:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,of the house
Dialogue: 0,1:01:43.43,1:01:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,seeming to know that this
Dialogue: 0,1:01:44.89,1:01:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,instant was ours alone. The
Dialogue: 0,1:01:46.46,1:01:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,corridor was dark except for the
Dialogue: 0,1:01:48.32,1:01:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,yellow
Dialogue: 0,1:01:48.67,1:01:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,light of the sconce at the end
Dialogue: 0,1:01:50.06,1:01:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,of the wall. And that light
Dialogue: 0,1:01:51.31,1:01:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,rested on his face in a way I
Dialogue: 0,1:01:52.65,1:01:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,wouldn't have
Dialogue: 0,1:01:53.25,1:01:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,had the courage to describe a
Dialogue: 0,1:01:55.45,1:01:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,loud. Then he kissed me. It was
Dialogue: 0,1:01:57.80,1:01:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,just one kiss. Slow, long,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:59.77,1:02:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,quiet,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:00.79,1:02:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,like someone finally saying a
Dialogue: 0,1:02:02.29,1:02:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,sentence he'd rehearsed for
Dialogue: 0,1:02:03.68,1:02:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,weeks, and discovered was
Dialogue: 0,1:02:04.97,1:02:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,simpler than
Dialogue: 0,1:02:05.59,1:02:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,he'd imagined. His hands slid
Dialogue: 0,1:02:07.31,1:02:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,down to my waist and stayed
Dialogue: 0,1:02:08.92,1:02:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,there with a firmness that
Dialogue: 0,1:02:10.46,1:02:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,wasn't urgency.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:11.35,1:02:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It was decision. Mine rose to
Dialogue: 0,1:02:13.09,1:02:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,the nape of his neck, and the
Dialogue: 0,1:02:14.83,1:02:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,door at the end of the left
Dialogue: 0,1:02:16.45,1:02:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,corridor
Dialogue: 0,1:02:16.93,1:02:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,opened behind him. I went in.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:18.90,1:02:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The door closed. I woke with sun
Dialogue: 0,1:02:21.08,1:02:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,on my face and didn't understand
Dialogue: 0,1:02:23.25,1:02:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,it first where I was. The window
Dialogue: 0,1:02:25.31,1:02:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,was different. Larger, facing
Dialogue: 0,1:02:27.18,1:02:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,the side garden I'd never seen
Dialogue: 0,1:02:29.11,1:02:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,from that angle. The curtains
Dialogue: 0,1:02:30.88,1:02:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,were heavy linen. The color of
Dialogue: 0,1:02:32.71,1:02:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,sand. Not the light white ones
Dialogue: 0,1:02:34.54,1:02:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,of my room.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:35.63,1:02:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The smell of the air was
Dialogue: 0,1:02:37.04,1:02:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,different, too. Dark wood.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:38.57,1:02:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Something citrusy and clean that
Dialogue: 0,1:02:40.44,1:02:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd already
Dialogue: 0,1:02:41.09,1:02:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,learn to associate with him
Dialogue: 0,1:02:42.46,1:02:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,without realizing when I'd
Dialogue: 0,1:02:43.77,1:02:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,learned it. And there was a hand
Dialogue: 0,1:02:45.39,1:02:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,on my back,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:46.37,1:02:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,broad, warm, resting on my spine
Dialogue: 0,1:02:48.26,1:02:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,with the calm of someone who
Dialogue: 0,1:02:49.91,1:02:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,didn't intend to leave anytime
Dialogue: 0,1:02:51.68,1:02:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,soon.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:52.37,1:02:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I turned slowly. Ludovica was
Dialogue: 0,1:02:54.27,1:02:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,awake, propped on his elbow.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:56.10,1:02:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Looking at me the way a person
Dialogue: 0,1:02:58.06,1:02:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,looks when
Dialogue: 0,1:02:58.71,1:03:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,they finally allowed themselves
Dialogue: 0,1:03:00.60,1:03:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,to look, without controlling,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:02.36,1:03:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,without calculating. Just
Dialogue: 0,1:03:03.88,1:03:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,looking.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:04.97,1:03:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,As if I were a problem he'd
Dialogue: 0,1:03:06.58,1:03:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,given up solving and decided
Dialogue: 0,1:03:08.25,1:03:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,simply to have. Good morning. He
Dialogue: 0,1:03:10.15,1:03:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,said,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:10.45,1:03:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,his voice horse from morning.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:12.27,1:03:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Deeper than usual. Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:14.27,1:03:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,He ran his thumb over the corner
Dialogue: 0,1:03:16.28,1:03:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,of my
Dialogue: 0,1:03:16.59,1:03:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,mouth. I don't know what he was
Dialogue: 0,1:03:18.13,1:03:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,checking, but he did it with the
Dialogue: 0,1:03:19.72,1:03:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,attention of someone verifying
Dialogue: 0,1:03:21.21,1:03:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,that
Dialogue: 0,1:03:21.41,1:03:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,something is still real. Half a
Dialogue: 0,1:03:23.23,1:03:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,laugh of mine escaped before I
Dialogue: 0,1:03:24.99,1:03:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,decided to let it. What is it?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:27.01,1:03:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm trying to remember the name
Dialogue: 0,1:03:29.00,1:03:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,of my room. I said, I think I
Dialogue: 0,1:03:30.86,1:03:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,forgot. He laughed low. It was a
Dialogue: 0,1:03:32.91,1:03:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,sound
Dialogue: 0,1:03:33.23,1:03:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd heard very few times. And
Dialogue: 0,1:03:35.09,1:03:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,that, that morning, seemed to
Dialogue: 0,1:03:36.95,1:03:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,open something in his chest.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:38.75,1:03:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Something
Dialogue: 0,1:03:39.33,1:03:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,he'd kept closed for a long
Dialogue: 0,1:03:40.83,1:03:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,time. And now let out through
Dialogue: 0,1:03:42.45,1:03:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,that small crack. There was a
Dialogue: 0,1:03:44.06,1:03:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,knock at the door
Dialogue: 0,1:03:45.01,1:03:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,with two discrete taps. Dona
Dialogue: 0,1:03:46.88,1:03:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Chiara's voice, from outside,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:48.81,1:03:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,crossed the wood with the same
Dialogue: 0,1:03:50.81,1:03:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,professional
Dialogue: 0,1:03:51.61,1:03:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,serenity as always. Coffee sir
Dialogue: 0,1:03:53.47,1:03:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and madam. The tray is out here
Dialogue: 0,1:03:55.38,1:03:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,when you want it. I heard the
Dialogue: 0,1:03:57.18,1:03:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,sound of
Dialogue: 0,1:03:57.67,1:03:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,her footsteps moving away down
Dialogue: 0,1:03:59.19,1:04:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,the corridor, with a short pause
Dialogue: 0,1:04:00.82,1:04:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,at the end before she
Dialogue: 0,1:04:01.88,1:04:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:03.23,1:04:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly the length of a
Dialogue: 0,1:04:04.60,1:04:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,contained smile. Calculated not
Dialogue: 0,1:04:06.46,1:04:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,to be heard, and completely
Dialogue: 0,1:04:08.07,1:04:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,audible
Dialogue: 0,1:04:09.49,1:04:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Ludovico got up, put on his
Dialogue: 0,1:04:10.82,1:04:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,white shirt without buttoning
Dialogue: 0,1:04:12.26,1:04:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,it, went to the door and came
Dialogue: 0,1:04:13.69,1:04:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,back with the
Dialogue: 0,1:04:14.33,1:04:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,tray. Two fine porcelain cups, a
Dialogue: 0,1:04:16.60,1:04:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,saucer with thin biscuits, and
Dialogue: 0,1:04:18.72,1:04:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,my cup already set with two
Dialogue: 0,1:04:20.64,1:04:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,cubes
Dialogue: 0,1:04:20.99,1:04:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,in a drop of milk. I put both
Dialogue: 0,1:04:22.65,1:04:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,hands around it and said
Dialogue: 0,1:04:24.02,1:04:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,nothing. The warmth passed
Dialogue: 0,1:04:25.50,1:04:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,through the
Dialogue: 0,1:04:26.13,1:04:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,porcelain and warmed my palms.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:28.23,1:04:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,He saw that I saw. She knows
Dialogue: 0,1:04:30.20,1:04:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,that I know. He said, sitting
Dialogue: 0,1:04:32.23,1:04:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,again on
Dialogue: 0,1:04:32.79,1:04:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,the edge of the bed. I left it
Dialogue: 0,1:04:34.60,1:04:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,noted on the first day. I know
Dialogue: 0,1:04:36.42,1:04:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,you did. We drank the coffee
Dialogue: 0,1:04:38.11,1:04:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,without hurry. Through the
Dialogue: 0,1:04:39.73,1:04:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,window of his room, the side
Dialogue: 0,1:04:41.47,1:04:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,garden appeared whole. The
Dialogue: 0,1:04:43.08,1:04:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,hedges still
Dialogue: 0,1:04:43.83,1:04:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,with dew caught in the leaves.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:45.53,1:04:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The morning light cutting
Dialogue: 0,1:04:46.95,1:04:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,through everything at a
Dialogue: 0,1:04:48.25,1:04:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,diagonal. It was a
Dialogue: 0,1:04:49.27,1:04:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,different view from the one in
Dialogue: 0,1:04:51.03,1:04:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,my room. More open. Deeper. I
Dialogue: 0,1:04:52.74,1:04:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,thought it would take me a while
Dialogue: 0,1:04:54.62,1:04:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,to get
Dialogue: 0,1:04:54.97,1:04:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,used to it. Then I realized I
Dialogue: 0,1:04:56.73,1:04:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,was getting used to it now. We
Dialogue: 0,1:04:58.55,1:05:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,went down together afterward.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:00.31,1:05:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Bastion
Dialogue: 0,1:05:00.73,1:05:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,was crossing the hall with a
Dialogue: 0,1:05:02.15,1:05:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,folder under his arm, and the
Dialogue: 0,1:05:03.63,1:05:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,sure step of someone who has
Dialogue: 0,1:05:05.06,1:05:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,three
Dialogue: 0,1:05:05.31,1:05:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,tasks to solve before 10 in the
Dialogue: 0,1:05:07.03,1:05:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,morning. When he saw us come
Dialogue: 0,1:05:08.59,1:05:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,down side by side on the stairs,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:10.85,1:05:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,he stopped for a third of a
Dialogue: 0,1:05:12.25,1:05:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,second. The corner of his eye
Dialogue: 0,1:05:13.75,1:05:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,betrayed half a millimeter of
Dialogue: 0,1:05:15.25,1:05:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,curiosity,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:16.43,1:05:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,and he kept walking toward the
Dialogue: 0,1:05:17.93,1:05:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,library without breaking his
Dialogue: 0,1:05:19.33,1:05:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,step. I thought I was going to
Dialogue: 0,1:05:20.83,1:05:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,laugh.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:21.57,1:05:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I held it. Dona Kiarra passed us
Dialogue: 0,1:05:23.44,1:05:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,in the kitchen corridor,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:24.85,1:05:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,carrying a basket of flowers cut
Dialogue: 0,1:05:26.72,1:05:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,from the
Dialogue: 0,1:05:27.19,1:05:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,garden. White hydranges and
Dialogue: 0,1:05:28.83,1:05:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,sprigs of rosemary and said,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:30.53,1:05:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,good morning, sir, and madam,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:32.29,1:05:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,with the same neutral intonation
Dialogue: 0,1:05:34.08,1:05:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,as always, except for the corner
Dialogue: 0,1:05:35.88,1:05:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,of her mouth that was making
Dialogue: 0,1:05:37.45,1:05:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,a visible and silent effort to
Dialogue: 0,1:05:39.27,1:05:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,stay still. Ludovico squeezed my
Dialogue: 0,1:05:41.21,1:05:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,hand inside his more firmly.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:43.41,1:05:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,His fingers interlacing mine,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:45.06,1:05:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,and made no comment. We
Dialogue: 0,1:05:46.37,1:05:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,continued down the corridor
Dialogue: 0,1:05:47.90,1:05:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,toward the
Dialogue: 0,1:05:48.47,1:05:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,garden as if coming down the
Dialogue: 0,1:05:49.73,1:05:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,stairs together on a Saturday
Dialogue: 0,1:05:51.04,1:05:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,morning where the most natural
Dialogue: 0,1:05:52.39,1:05:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,thing in
Dialogue: 0,1:05:52.75,1:05:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,the world. Maybe it already was.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:55.03,1:05:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Outside, the day had dawned
Dialogue: 0,1:05:56.95,1:05:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,clear, with that firm winter
Dialogue: 0,1:05:58.95,1:05:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,blue
Dialogue: 0,1:05:59.23,1:06:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,that promises no warmth but
Dialogue: 0,1:06:00.73,1:06:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,delivers light to spare. The
Dialogue: 0,1:06:02.29,1:06:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,leaves still wet from the
Dialogue: 0,1:06:03.68,1:06:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,previous
Dialogue: 0,1:06:04.13,1:06:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,night's drizzle glistened. The
Dialogue: 0,1:06:05.90,1:06:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,air smelled of damp earth, and
Dialogue: 0,1:06:07.67,1:06:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,the thin smoke of coffee rising
Dialogue: 0,1:06:09.49,1:06:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,from
Dialogue: 0,1:06:09.73,1:06:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,the open kitchen. He led me to
Dialogue: 0,1:06:11.70,1:06:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,the stone bench beneath the
Dialogue: 0,1:06:13.47,1:06:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Magnolia. Satt pulled me to sit
Dialogue: 0,1:06:15.51,1:06:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,beside him,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:16.39,1:06:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,and kept my hand inside his on
Dialogue: 0,1:06:18.68,1:06:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,his knee. No tie. No audience.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:20.97,1:06:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,No contract. Just the hand,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:23.43,1:06:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and the cold bench beneath us,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:24.96,1:06:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,and the light hitting the
Dialogue: 0,1:06:26.24,1:06:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Magnolia leaves that still had
Dialogue: 0,1:06:27.77,1:06:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,late blossoms
Dialogue: 0,1:06:28.43,1:06:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,high in the branches. It's the
Dialogue: 0,1:06:30.27,1:06:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,first time, I said low, that I
Dialogue: 0,1:06:32.12,1:06:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,hold you in public without it
Dialogue: 0,1:06:33.90,1:06:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,being
Dialogue: 0,1:06:34.21,1:06:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,for appearances. Yes, he didn't
Dialogue: 0,1:06:36.35,1:06:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,answer. He just squeezed gently.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:38.56,1:06:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,His thumb passing over my
Dialogue: 0,1:06:40.28,1:06:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,knuckles once.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:41.67,1:06:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,We stayed there a good while,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:43.18,1:06:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,without needing to fill it. A
Dialogue: 0,1:06:44.69,1:06:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,swallow landed on the edge of
Dialogue: 0,1:06:46.20,1:06:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,the stone
Dialogue: 0,1:06:46.67,1:06:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,fountain, drank, and flew away.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:48.43,1:06:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The mansion's kitchen led out
Dialogue: 0,1:06:50.07,1:06:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,the smell of hot bread through
Dialogue: 0,1:06:51.78,1:06:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,the open
Dialogue: 0,1:06:52.23,1:06:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,window, something in my chest,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:53.93,1:06:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,which I'd been carrying clenched
Dialogue: 0,1:06:55.74,1:06:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,since the church bell,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:56.99,1:06:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,since the collector days of the
Dialogue: 0,1:06:58.72,1:07:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,door. Since the afternoon I
Dialogue: 0,1:07:00.22,1:07:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,signed a contract just to have
Dialogue: 0,1:07:01.89,1:07:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,somewhere to sleep, began to
Dialogue: 0,1:07:04.06,1:07:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,loosen slowly, not all at once.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:06.47,1:07:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Slowly, like a knot that
Dialogue: 0,1:07:08.33,1:07:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,eased after being tied too tight
Dialogue: 0,1:07:10.15,1:07:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,for too long. Bastian came up
Dialogue: 0,1:07:11.79,1:07:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,the stone path with a firmer
Dialogue: 0,1:07:13.38,1:07:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,step
Dialogue: 0,1:07:13.61,1:07:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,than usual. He had an envelope
Dialogue: 0,1:07:15.59,1:07:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,in his hand. Ludovico raised his
Dialogue: 0,1:07:17.69,1:07:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,head, and I saw the exact moment
Dialogue: 0,1:07:19.80,1:07:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,he
Dialogue: 0,1:07:19.93,1:07:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,saw the envelope. His body
Dialogue: 0,1:07:21.79,1:07:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,changed. Not much, just in the
Dialogue: 0,1:07:23.94,1:07:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,shoulders, in the line of his
Dialogue: 0,1:07:26.02,1:07:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,jaw,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:26.31,1:07:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,in a way of straightening his
Dialogue: 0,1:07:28.20,1:07:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,spine that wasn't posture. It
Dialogue: 0,1:07:30.09,1:07:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,was alertness. It just arrived.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:32.83,1:07:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Bastian said, handing the
Dialogue: 0,1:07:34.64,1:07:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,envelope into his hand. Man on a
Dialogue: 0,1:07:36.97,1:07:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,motorcycle didn't stop. Ludovico
Dialogue: 0,1:07:39.29,1:07:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,turned the envelope over. It was
Dialogue: 0,1:07:41.20,1:07:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,old. The darkened cream color of
Dialogue: 0,1:07:43.12,1:07:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,something that had spent time
Dialogue: 0,1:07:44.85,1:07:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,kept in a drawer or a safe. And
Dialogue: 0,1:07:46.81,1:07:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,on the back there was a red wax
Dialogue: 0,1:07:48.77,1:07:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,seal with the split crown
Dialogue: 0,1:07:50.35,1:07:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,lion crest stamped deep and with
Dialogue: 0,1:07:52.61,1:07:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,precision. The same crest is the
Dialogue: 0,1:07:54.87,1:07:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Elder's Rings. The same as
Dialogue: 0,1:07:56.71,1:07:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,the Manchins main gate. Except
Dialogue: 0,1:07:58.50,1:08:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,that seal seemed older than the
Dialogue: 0,1:08:00.36,1:08:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Rings. Older than the library's
Dialogue: 0,1:08:02.21,1:08:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,dark wood. Older than anything
Dialogue: 0,1:08:03.89,1:08:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd touched in that house. He
Dialogue: 0,1:08:05.51,1:08:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,looked at the crest for two
Dialogue: 0,1:08:07.02,1:08:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,seconds
Dialogue: 0,1:08:07.41,1:08:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,longer than he should have. The
Dialogue: 0,1:08:09.07,1:08:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,garden was quiet. The swallow
Dialogue: 0,1:08:10.63,1:08:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,came back to the fountain and
Dialogue: 0,1:08:12.19,1:08:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,flew away
Dialogue: 0,1:08:12.67,1:08:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,again. Then he closed his hand
Dialogue: 0,1:08:14.55,1:08:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,around the envelope carefully.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:16.42,1:08:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you Bastian. Bastian
Dialogue: 0,1:08:18.05,1:08:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,nodded and went back up the
Dialogue: 0,1:08:19.58,1:08:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,stone path with nothing more.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:21.23,1:08:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Ludovico stood up. I'll be right
Dialogue: 0,1:08:23.05,1:08:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,back.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:23.75,1:08:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I followed him with my eyes down
Dialogue: 0,1:08:25.42,1:08:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,the covered corridor to the
Dialogue: 0,1:08:26.83,1:08:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,office. The door closed with a
Dialogue: 0,1:08:28.40,1:08:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,soft
Dialogue: 0,1:08:28.61,1:08:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,click. I sat on the bench. My
Dialogue: 0,1:08:30.55,1:08:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,hand marked by the warmth of
Dialogue: 0,1:08:32.42,1:08:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,his. Watching the swallow land
Dialogue: 0,1:08:34.42,1:08:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,for the
Dialogue: 0,1:08:34.89,1:08:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,third time on the edge of the
Dialogue: 0,1:08:36.47,1:08:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,fountain. I mentally counted the
Dialogue: 0,1:08:38.22,1:08:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,seconds without meaning to
Dialogue: 0,1:08:39.64,1:08:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,count. He
Dialogue: 0,1:08:40.13,1:08:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,came back at 42, without the
Dialogue: 0,1:08:41.94,1:08:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,envelope. With his hands in his
Dialogue: 0,1:08:43.93,1:08:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,pockets, his shoulders slightly
Dialogue: 0,1:08:45.93,1:08:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,lowered.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:46.45,1:08:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,His face composed back into the
Dialogue: 0,1:08:48.32,1:08:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,expression I'd learned to read
Dialogue: 0,1:08:50.12,1:08:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,beneath. He sat again beside me.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:52.27,1:08:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,He took my hand again. Firmer
Dialogue: 0,1:08:53.99,1:08:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,this time. Two firm for a
Dialogue: 0,1:08:55.48,1:08:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Saturday morning that until a
Dialogue: 0,1:08:57.20,1:08:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,minute ago
Dialogue: 0,1:08:57.79,1:08:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,had been going very well. What
Dialogue: 0,1:08:59.60,1:09:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,was it? I asked low. Nothing
Dialogue: 0,1:09:01.28,1:09:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,that needs to reach you today.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:03.61,1:09:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I looked at him. He held my gaze
Dialogue: 0,1:09:05.59,1:09:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,without looking away. And I saw
Dialogue: 0,1:09:07.50,1:09:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,both things at once. The truth
Dialogue: 0,1:09:09.35,1:09:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,about it not being today. And
Dialogue: 0,1:09:11.18,1:09:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,the lie about it being nothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:13.13,1:09:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Two distinct things. Living in
Dialogue: 0,1:09:15.02,1:09:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,the
Dialogue: 0,1:09:15.21,1:09:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,same sentence. In the same dark
Dialogue: 0,1:09:17.17,1:09:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,eyes I'd already learned not to
Dialogue: 0,1:09:19.14,1:09:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,underestimate. I could ask.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:21.37,1:09:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I could insist. I could get up
Dialogue: 0,1:09:22.91,1:09:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,from there and go to the office
Dialogue: 0,1:09:24.51,1:09:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,drawer and open the envelope
Dialogue: 0,1:09:25.95,1:09:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,myself.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:26.71,1:09:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that this house's door was
Dialogue: 0,1:09:28.61,1:09:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,mine, too. I had that right. I
Dialogue: 0,1:09:30.52,1:09:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,didn't. I chose to stay at
Dialogue: 0,1:09:32.17,1:09:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,peace for one morning. A whole
Dialogue: 0,1:09:34.12,1:09:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,morning. Without a knot in my
Dialogue: 0,1:09:36.01,1:09:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,chest. Without a collector.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:37.77,1:09:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Without a bell.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:39.23,1:09:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd earned the right to choose
Dialogue: 0,1:09:41.09,1:09:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,this. All right. I said, he
Dialogue: 0,1:09:42.76,1:09:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,squeezed my hand again.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:44.19,1:09:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Then he relaxed his grip. And we
Dialogue: 0,1:09:46.26,1:09:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,stayed there a while longer. On
Dialogue: 0,1:09:48.26,1:09:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,the bench. Benete the Magnollia.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:50.83,1:09:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,With the smell of the kitchens
Dialogue: 0,1:09:52.25,1:09:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,bread arriving through the
Dialogue: 0,1:09:53.47,1:09:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,window. And the swallow coming
Dialogue: 0,1:09:54.89,1:09:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,back a
Dialogue: 0,1:09:55.17,1:09:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,fourth time as if it too were in
Dialogue: 0,1:09:56.94,1:09:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,no hurry to go anywhere. We went
Dialogue: 0,1:09:58.70,1:10:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,to the winter garden late in the
Dialogue: 0,1:10:00.47,1:10:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,morning. He brought a book. I
Dialogue: 0,1:10:02.39,1:10:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,brought another. The space was
Dialogue: 0,1:10:04.37,1:10:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,made of glass and iron. Full of
Dialogue: 0,1:10:06.41,1:10:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,plants
Dialogue: 0,1:10:06.81,1:10:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,don't a GR attended with an
Dialogue: 0,1:10:08.25,1:10:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,attention I'd never seen
Dialogue: 0,1:10:09.53,1:10:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,dedicated to plants. And the
Dialogue: 0,1:10:11.02,1:10:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,light came in
Dialogue: 0,1:10:11.71,1:10:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,from every side at once. Warm
Dialogue: 0,1:10:13.62,1:10:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,and diffuse even in winter. I
Dialogue: 0,1:10:15.52,1:10:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,sat on the long sofa near the
Dialogue: 0,1:10:17.43,1:10:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,largest pain where the sun hit
Dialogue: 0,1:10:19.42,1:10:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,hardest. He sat in the armchair
Dialogue: 0,1:10:21.47,1:10:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,beside me. Stretched out his
Dialogue: 0,1:10:23.33,1:10:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,hand
Dialogue: 0,1:10:23.59,1:10:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,without looking and rested his
Dialogue: 0,1:10:25.36,1:10:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,fingers on my ankle. The gesture
Dialogue: 0,1:10:27.24,1:10:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,no longer asked permission.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:29.45,1:10:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't take his hand away. I
Dialogue: 0,1:10:31.30,1:10:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,read two pages without
Dialogue: 0,1:10:32.61,1:10:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,understanding anything. I reread
Dialogue: 0,1:10:34.51,1:10:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,them.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:35.07,1:10:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I understood. The light came in
Dialogue: 0,1:10:36.62,1:10:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,through the pains and fell on
Dialogue: 0,1:10:38.07,1:10:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,the broad leaves of the plants
Dialogue: 0,1:10:39.57,1:10:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,in
Dialogue: 0,1:10:39.67,1:10:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,bleak, slow bands. And I thought
Dialogue: 0,1:10:41.69,1:10:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,without meaning to think it that
Dialogue: 0,1:10:43.71,1:10:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,he'd put away that envelope
Dialogue: 0,1:10:45.41,1:10:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,too carefully for it to be
Dialogue: 0,1:10:46.96,1:10:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,nothing. That his hand was too
Dialogue: 0,1:10:48.75,1:10:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,firm to be just a Saturday
Dialogue: 0,1:10:50.29,1:10:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,morning.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:51.57,1:10:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I let the thought pass. Not
Dialogue: 0,1:10:53.42,1:10:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,because I believed it. Because
Dialogue: 0,1:10:55.48,1:10:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,today his hand was on my ankle.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:58.07,1:10:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And the sun was good. And I'd
Dialogue: 0,1:10:59.65,1:11:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,climb the stairs the night
Dialogue: 0,1:11:01.07,1:11:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,before without a contract. And
Dialogue: 0,1:11:02.71,1:11:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,this
Dialogue: 0,1:11:02.93,1:11:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,morning was mine. Tomorrow I
Dialogue: 0,1:11:04.88,1:11:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,would ask. Tomorrow if he didn't
Dialogue: 0,1:11:07.10,1:11:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,tell me I'd go after it. I'd
Dialogue: 0,1:11:09.04,1:11:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,already
Dialogue: 0,1:11:09.53,1:11:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,learn to go after things. And
Dialogue: 0,1:11:11.14,1:11:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd already learned that the
Dialogue: 0,1:11:12.69,1:11:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,truth doesn't disappear. It only
Dialogue: 0,1:11:14.47,1:11:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,waits. For today, I stayed. I
Dialogue: 0,1:11:16.56,1:11:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,thought the greatest danger of
Dialogue: 0,1:11:18.72,1:11:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,my life had been hiring ever
Dialogue: 0,1:11:20.73,1:11:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and for one night. But I was
Dialogue: 0,1:11:22.96,1:11:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,wrong. The real danger began
Dialogue: 0,1:11:25.20,1:11:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,when I started to believe that,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:27.67,1:11:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,by his
Dialogue: 0,1:11:28.15,1:11:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,side, I could finally be happy.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:30.68,1:11:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,He loved me without hiding it,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:33.13,1:11:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,protected me without confining
Dialogue: 0,1:11:35.58,1:11:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,me.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:36.59,1:11:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,His arms around me felt like the
Dialogue: 0,1:11:38.46,1:11:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,only safe place in the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:41.31,1:11:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Until I found the envelope
Dialogue: 0,1:11:43.18,1:11:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,hidden in his drawer. Three
Dialogue: 0,1:11:45.12,1:11:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,photos. My face marked on the
Dialogue: 0,1:11:47.20,1:11:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,screen of a
Dialogue: 0,1:11:47.99,1:11:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,news report that hadn't yet
Dialogue: 0,1:11:49.67,1:11:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,aired. A transfer receipt with
Dialogue: 0,1:11:51.54,1:11:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,the exact date of the worst
Dialogue: 0,1:11:53.21,1:11:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,night of my life
Dialogue: 0,1:11:54.21,1:11:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and a message from him. Short
Dialogue: 0,1:11:56.92,1:11:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,sent to a number I didn't
Dialogue: 0,1:11:59.25,1:12:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,recognize. She can't find out.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:02.77,1:12:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Within a few hours, my life
Dialogue: 0,1:12:04.72,1:12:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,became a headline. The same
Dialogue: 0,1:12:06.66,1:12:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,people who'd applauded me now
Dialogue: 0,1:12:08.75,1:12:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,looked at me like an accomplice.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:10.80,1:12:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Dores slammed in my face. Voices
Dialogue: 0,1:12:12.84,1:12:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,accused me terribly of something
Dialogue: 0,1:12:14.89,1:12:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't even understand. An
Dialogue: 0,1:12:16.88,1:12:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,evern, the man who swore to
Dialogue: 0,1:12:18.80,1:12:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,protect me, disappeared for
Dialogue: 0,1:12:20.72,1:12:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,hours,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:21.39,1:12:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,and came back with a look I
Dialogue: 0,1:12:23.03,1:12:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,couldn't decipher. I wanted to
Dialogue: 0,1:12:24.85,1:12:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,trust him. But every silence
Dialogue: 0,1:12:26.55,1:12:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,of his
Dialogue: 0,1:12:32.03,1:12:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,eye, now I have to choose. Flee,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:34.31,1:12:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,before he drags me down with
Dialogue: 0,1:12:36.31,1:12:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,him. Or stay by the side of the
Dialogue: 0,1:12:38.52,1:12:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,man
Dialogue: 0,1:12:38.73,1:12:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,who may have orchestrated the
Dialogue: 0,1:12:40.31,1:12:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,night that nearly destroyed me.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:42.01,1:12:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And what if the love that saved
Dialogue: 0,1:12:43.70,1:12:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,me
Dialogue: 0,1:12:43.81,1:12:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,is the same one that planned my
Dialogue: 0,1:12:45.81,1:12:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,ruin? And what if every, I love
Dialogue: 0,1:12:47.81,1:12:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,you of his was just the price to
Dialogue: 0,1:12:49.87,1:12:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,keep me quiet? And what if, in
Dialogue: 0,1:12:51.67,1:12:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,the end, the escort I rented
Dialogue: 0,1:12:53.35,1:12:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,never stopped being the mafia
Dialogue: 0,1:12:55.09,1:12:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,boss
Dialogue: 0,1:12:55.33,1:12:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,the entire country fears? Like I
Dialogue: 0,1:12:57.23,1:12:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,said, that was just a taste of
Dialogue: 0,1:12:59.01,1:13:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,book two. To watch it
Dialogue: 0,1:13:00.26,1:13:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,uncensored,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:00.91,1:13:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,just click on the first link
Dialogue: 0,1:13:02.31,1:13:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,here in the pinned comment. I'll
Dialogue: 0,1:13:03.92,1:13:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,see you on the other side in a
Dialogue: 0,1:13:05.42,1:13:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,few
Dialogue: 0,1:13:05.57,1:13:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,seconds. Remember, just click on
Dialogue: 0,1:13:07.51,1:13:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,the first link down here in the
Dialogue: 0,1:13:09.39,1:13:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,comments. And book two,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:11.17,1:13:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,complete. With no ads or
Dialogue: 0,1:13:12.61,1:13:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,interruptions, we'll already be
Dialogue: 0,1:13:14.47,1:13:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,available for you. It's very
Dialogue: 0,1:13:16.15,1:13:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,simple.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:17.05,1:13:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Book two is something I'm loving
Dialogue: 0,1:13:18.62,1:13:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,making, and you're loving it
Dialogue: 0,1:13:19.99,1:13:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,too, so I promise there will be
Dialogue: 0,1:13:21.51,1:13:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,more.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:21.97,1:13:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It's where you find increasingly
Dialogue: 0,1:13:23.95,1:13:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,spicy stories. A true dark
Dialogue: 0,1:13:25.56,1:13:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,romance. And precisely because
Dialogue: 0,1:13:27.41,1:13:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,this version is getting more and
Dialogue: 0,1:13:29.10,1:13:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,more heated, the video isn't
Dialogue: 0,1:13:30.57,1:13:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,well accepted publicly on
Dialogue: 0,1:13:31.89,1:13:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,YouTube.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:32.95,1:13:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,This closed environment is where
Dialogue: 0,1:13:34.72,1:13:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I can actually share my essence,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:36.49,1:13:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,and where I feel free to do my
Dialogue: 0,1:13:38.15,1:13:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,best
Dialogue: 0,1:13:38.37,1:13:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,work for you. More news coming
Dialogue: 0,1:13:39.77,1:13:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,soon. I'll be waiting for you on
Dialogue: 0,1:13:41.27,1:13:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,the other side.